(16, 'Silk Path Grand Sapa Resort & Spa', 'Doi Quan 6, Group 5, Sa Pa, Lào Cai 330000, Vietnam', 5, '02143788555', NULL, 'https://silkpathhotel.com/', '<p>5-star comfort awaits at Silk Path Grand Sapa Resort &amp; Spa, offering state-of-the-art facilities and cozy accommodations in Sapa Town. Guests can enjoy a dip in the indoor heated pool or relax with pampering massage at the spa. Free WiFi access is available in entire property. Adorned in neutral palette with accents of brown, blue and reddish orange from the fabrics, all rooms are elegantly design with dark wood furnishings. Fitted with large windows enjoying natural sun lights and mountain views, air-conditioned rooms have a private balcony, flat-screen TV and mini-bar. Certain rooms feature a separate seating and/or terrace. Private bathroom comes with a shower and bathtub. There is a 24-hour front desk, a shared lounge and gift shop at the property. Babysitting service is available at the kids\' club. Guests also enjoy some discount on spa treatment and karaoke per stay. Fansipan Mountain is 0.6 mi from Silk Path Grand Sapa Resort &amp; Spa, while Sa Pa Lake is 2953 feet away. Complimentary pick-up service from Sapa Stone Church to the hotel is provided. Your property description is created based on the facilities and amenities you add. It also includes info about nearby landmarks and attractions to make it stand out on search engines like Google. It&rsquo;s then translated into multiple languages, which can increase bookings by appealing to all potential guests. The average time for processing requests is 6 days</p>', 'hotels/January2024/JUwFrfwRq5wC161oZmww.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/L7DOtnjUro1uH5Fw8kj3.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:23:53', '2024-01-16 08:23:53', 1, 'silk-path-grand-sapa-resort-and-spa', NULL, '5-star comfort awaits at Silk Path Grand Sapa Resort & Spa, offering state-of-the-art facilities and cozy accommodations in Sapa Town. Guests can enjoy a dip in the indoor heated pool or relax wit