(18, 'Topas Ecolodge', 'Thanh Kim, Sa Pa, Lao Cai, Vietnam', 5, '02473070899', NULL, 'http://topasecolodge.com/', '<p>Lying within the boundaries and overlooking valleys of the Hoang Lien National Park, Topas Ecolodge is a quaint and charming mountain property where guests can freely mingle with the ethnic villagers. A free shuttle bus operates daily to and from Sa Pa Town, 11 mi away (Please reserve at least 24 hours in advance as there are limited seats and departures). Besides admiring the beautiful scenery, other activities include cycling and trekking or simply enjoying the free WiFi in the public areas. Granite walls and wooden furnishings add to the rustic feel of the guestrooms. Guests have a choice of heated or air-conditioned rooms, all equipped with a private bathroom and balcony to enjoy the views of the valley. Topas Ecolodge is located within Ban Lech Village overlooking Hoang Lien Mountain Range. It is 24 mi from Hoang Lien National Park Visitor Center, while Lao Cai Train Station is 33 mi away. A daily breakfast buffet is served at the lodge\'s restaurant. Asian dishes are also available throughout the day. Guests can also find a lounge with a bar. Day trips and packed lunches can be arranged at the tour desk. Valuables can be stored at the front desk\'s safety deposit boxes.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/Us2mrgWdSSq9EaIvFMwL.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/t6F74kLbNC3hZIKxx22O.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:26:35', '2024-01-16 08:26:35', 1, 'topas-ecolodge', NULL, 'Lying within the boundaries and overlooking valleys of the Hoang Lien National Park, Topas Ecolodge is a quaint and charming mountain property where guests can freely mingle with the ethnic villagers. A free shuttle bus operates daily to and from Sa Pa Town, 11 mi away (Please reserve at least 24 hours in advance as there are limited seats and departures). Besides admiring the beautiful scenery, other activities include cycling and trekking or simply enjoying the free WiFi in the public areas.', '<