(20, 'Hotel de la Coupole - MGallery', '1, Hoang Lien Street Sapa District, Lao Cai Province Sapa, 033000, Vietnam', 5, '02143629999', NULL, 'https://www.hoteldelacoupole.com/?y_source=1_MTUzNTk5NzAtNzE1LWxvY2F0aW9uLndlYnNpdGU%3D', '<p>Inspired from the minority tribes in Sapa and French Haute Couture, all rooms at the property offer a balcony, air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kettle, a hot tub, free toiletries and a wardrobe. Rooms are fitted with a private bathroom, while some feature a garden view. All guest rooms are equipped with a seating area. The hotel offers a continental or buffet breakfast. Guests can grab a bite to eat in the on-site restaurant, Chic - a french restaurant open all day also offering local Vietnamese cuisine. Cacao is the patisserie featuring master-crafted Marou chocolate and pastries while Absinthe offers champagne, tapas and crafted coctails for guests to enjoy. The property also has a sauna and a hammam. Guests at Hotel de la Coupole - MGallery will be able to enjoy activities in and around Sa Pa, like cycling. For any tips on how to get around or what to do in the area, guests can ask at the reception. The funicular station that transports guests to Fansipan cable car is located right outside the property. Sa Pa Bus Station is 1969 feet from the accommodations while Sa Pa Lake is less than 0.6 mi away. Sa Pa Central Square and Sa Pa Stone Church are reachable within a 4-minute walk and 1312 feet, respectively. The property is located 8.7 mi from Fansipan Mountain.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/V7MFlnPfegTXv5xt9aHI.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/hOPAw0QjwWLDLVcuP7N7.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:29:56', '2024-01-16 08:29:56', 1, 'hotel-de-la-coupole-mgallery', NULL, 'Inspired from the minority tribes in Sapa and French Haute Couture, all rooms at the property offer a balcony, air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kettle, a hot tub, free toiletries and a wardrobe. Rooms are fitted with a priv