(21, 'Wyndham Hoi An Royal Beachfront Resort', 'Block Ha My Dong A, Dien Duong Ward, Dien Ban Town, Tp. Hội An, Quảng Nam 560000, Việt Nam', 5, '02353939779', NULL, 'http://wyndhamroyalhoian.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Get the celebrity treatment with world-class service at Wyndham Hoi An Royal Beachfront Resort</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Facing the beachfront, Wyndham Hoi An Royal Beachfront Resort offers 5-star accommodations in Hoi An and has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center and garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and free shuttle service, along with free WiFi. Guests can have a drink at the bar. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a private bathroom with a shower. All rooms feature a closet. The daily breakfast offers buffet, &agrave; la carte or Full English/Irish options. Wyndham Hoi An Royal Beachfront Resort has a sun terrace. Ha My Beach is a 4-minute walk from the accommodation, while An Bang Beach is 0.8 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 13 miles from Wyndham Hoi An Royal Beachfront Resort.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/2kpAL6UAjXJh6XZjiDoe.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/DdxCZdIAQzej6Eh1pOKf.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 08:32:26', '2024-01-16 08:32:26', 1, 'wyn