(22, 'Diamond Nostalgia Hotel & Spa', '37 P. Mã Mây, Hàng Buồm, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội 111400, Vietnam', 3, '0858565998', NULL, 'http://diamondnostalgiahotel.com/', '<p>Attractively set in the Hoan Kiem district of Hanoi, Diamond Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa is located 656 feet from Hanoi Old City Gate, 1312 feet from Thang Long Water Puppet Theater and 1640 feet from Dong Xuan Market. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and a tour desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel has family rooms. All rooms have air-conditioned, working desk, a kettle, a fridge, a mini-bar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a bath. At Diamond Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa rooms come with bed linen and towels. Popular points of interest near Diamond Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa include Hoan Kiem Lake, St. Joseph Cathedral and Trang Tien Plaza. The nearest airport is Noi Bai International Airport, 16 mi from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/4x3WGKttRICn3liOyRK0.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/ZVKjrPIxMFEHDptqC8fd.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:34:54', '2024-01-16 08:38:49', 1, 'diamond-nostalgia-hotel-and-spa', NULL, 'Attractively set in the Hoan Kiem district of Hanoi, Diamond Nostalgia Hotel & Spa is located 656 feet from Hanoi Old City Gate, 1312 feet from Thang Long Water Puppet Theater and 1640 feet from Dong Xuan Market. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a 24-hour front desk and a tour desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3723.925798691876!2d105.8508609751531!3d21.03565478061532!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3135abbebc3b7b25%3A0xa98e1c3ae10eba19!2sHanoi%20Old%20Quarter%20Hostel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705394278893!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\