(25, 'Hanoi Nostalgia Hotel & Spa', '13-15 P. Lương Ngọc Quyến, Hàng Buồm, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội, Vietnam', 3, '02439263636', NULL, 'http://www.hanoinostalgiahotel.com/', '<p>Hanoi Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa features an outdoor swimming pool, garden, a shared lounge and terrace in Hanoi. This 3-star hotel offers an ATM and a concierge service. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi. At the hotel each room has air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Rooms are equipped with an electric tea pot, while selected rooms are equipped with a balcony and others also offer city views. At Hanoi Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa every room has bed linen and towels. A buffet, Full English/Irish or American breakfast is available daily at the property. At the accommodation you\'ll find a restaurant serving American, Chinese and Vietnamese cuisine. A vegetarian option can also be requested. Popular points of interest near Hanoi Nostalgia Hotel &amp; Spa include Hanoi Old City Gate, Hoan Kiem Lake and Thang Long Water Puppet Theater. The nearest airport is Noi Bai International Airport, 14 miles from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/w4tphERDqJ4AIiX8lzPM.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/ZYZ6oU6ZQNwdEMRON3V1.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:40:15', '2024-01-16 08:40:15', 1, 'hanoi-nostalgia-hotel-and-spa', NULL, 'Hanoi Nostalgia Hotel & Spa features an outdoor swimming pool, garden, a shared lounge and terrace in Hanoi. This 3-star hotel offers an ATM and a concierge service. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3723.949139060454!2d105.85045127515305!3d21.03472098061603!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3135abc0a2821c67%3A0x49f6ca6f8f6fd2fd!2sHanoi%20Nostalgia%20Hotel%20%26%20Spa!5