(26, 'La Siesta Hoi An Resort & Spa', '132 Hùng Vương, Phường Cẩm Phổ, Hội An, Quảng Nam 560000, Việt Nam', 4, '02353915913', NULL, 'https://lasiestaresorts.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience World-class Service at La Siesta Hoi An Resort &amp; Spa</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at La Siesta Hoi An Resort &amp; Spa! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?bkng_action=hotel&amp;lang=en-us&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;dt=1705394423&amp;state=UoICXk7utcQPMgAHLSdwsmEAhCEVeFNBFUe0yDOYq1bkATAD-Qk0f8Uk0sbtza8g6X6jN6kn6udA0zL0-ShPc7ik-18yp-gRyz5boCfVLokK5h_BEg4xVV00iAIzVUo2WYbnIlnuOeGT8FKAvjNG86w4J1IRLIg9rFc0YQmOYTI0dGVPeL-Kp3fF16jMlavTNzQCmmL1lBu0jntDeIpWM6kASiuAM7N-tZKJPQQlJMEDX8upt20JWtsMXj44KTX3IYKWpwBgMDZOYfCVIMqbpkWyEfaPkVWbgwHZ5ReD8AqIV1ffL09Ga6D1NQhh4PdTBm7yga1FHjytbRuFenHcRmuecMi3&amp;aid=357028&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;response_type=sso\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Boasting a 1312 ft&sup2; salt water pool, 200m2 infinity pool, a kid pool and a 328 ft&sup2; fresh water pool, Hoi An La Siesta Resort &amp; Spa is spread over 2 wings in Hoi An. The fashionably traditional Classic wing offers 70 rooms, while the club wing accommodates 67 classic suites with the old town\'s characteristics. Guests can pamper themselves in a pampering massage at the spa, or relax in the garden. Free WiFi throughout the property and free use of bicycles are available. All air-conditioned rooms feature a private balcony or a window that opens up to views of the swimming pool| the lush green garden| the rice field. A flat-screen TV with cable channels, as well as a laptop are available. All rooms are fitted with a private bathroom with standing shower or a bath. For your comfort, you will find bathrobes, slippers and free toiletries. Red Bean Restaurant serves a range of Asian dishes, while The Temple Restaurant features European cuisine. Room service is available upon request. Assembly Hall of the Cantonese Chinese Congregation and the Japanese Covered Bridge are 0.7 mi from Hoi An La Siesta Resort &amp; Spa, while Hoi An Ancient Town is 2297 feet away. Da Nang International Airport is 19 mi from the property. The property offers complimentary shuttle service to Old Town and An Bang Beach.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.2</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/ZY0UtkcJQgLFbU2WJz8w.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/FaaZJs4Oo3IeJAaFuvuF.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 08:42:25', '2024-01-16 08:42:25', 1, 'la-siesta-hoi-an-resort-and-spa', NULL, 'Boasting a 1312 ft² salt water pool, 200m2 infinity pool, a kid pool and a 328 ft² fresh water pool, Hoi An La Siesta Resort & Spa is spread over 2 wings in Hoi An. The fashionably traditional  Classic wing offers 70 rooms, while the club wing accommodates 67 classic suites with the old town\'s characteristics. Guests can pamper themselves in a pampering massage at the spa, or relax in the garden. Free WiFi throughout the property and free use of bicycles are available.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3837.55418350113!2d108.31381327414641!3d15.880011784772387!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31420f20fc490bfd%3A0xf39