(27, 'Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel', '43 P. Hàng Đồng, Hàng Bồ, Hoàn Kiếm, Hà Nội, Vietnam', 3, '0946683179', NULL, NULL, '<p>Set in the Hoan Kiem district in Hanoi, 984 feet from Dong Xuan Market, Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel features views of the city. Free WiFi is provided throughout the property. Guests can opt in a complimentary cooking class. Every room at this hotel is air-conditioned and is fitted with a flat-screen cable TV, mini-bar and electric kettle. Private bathroom is fitted with a bath or shower and a hairdryer. For your comfort, you will find bathrobes, slippers and free toiletries. Towels and linen are provided. Old City Gate is 1640 feet from Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel, while Ngoc Son Temple is 2625 feet away. The nearest airport is Noi Bai International Airport, 12 mi from Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel. Airport shuttle is available at a surcharge. You will find a 24-hour front desk which can assist guests with currency exchange, luggage storage and tour arrangements. You will find an ATM on site. Other facilities at Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel include a shared kitchen and shared lounge. The hotel also offers bike hire. Guests can enjoy the on-site restaurant. Room service and special diet menus are available upon request.</p>', NULL, '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/NoTgQJpGmbAmVJ11nWJT.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:42:43', '2024-01-16 08:42:43', 0, 'hanoi-golden-holiday-hotel', NULL, 'Set in the Hoan Kiem district in Hanoi, 984 feet from Dong Xuan Market, Hanoi Golden Holiday Hotel features views of the city. Free WiFi is provided throughout the property. Guests can opt in a complimentary cooking cla', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3723.924132734173!2d105.84281918004872!3d21.035721430633316!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3135abbeb135e9f7%3A0xb99aa84c13294ecf!2sHanoi%20Golden%20Holiday%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705394533417!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\"