(28, 'Fusion Suites Vung Tau', '2 Trương Công Định, Phường 1, Thành phố Vũng Tầu, Bà Rịa - Vũng Tàu, Vietnam', 0, '02546257272', NULL, 'https://vungtau.fusion-suites.com/', '<p>Located in Vung Tau, a 5-minute walk from Front Beach, Fusion Suites Vung Tau provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers room service, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi. Certain rooms at the property include a balcony with a city view. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, an electric tea pot, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. Certain rooms include a kitchen with a fridge, an oven and a microwave. At Fusion Suites Vung Tau each room comes with bed linen and towels. A buffet breakfast is available daily at the accommodation. At Fusion Suites Vung Tau you\'ll find a restaurant serving Vietnamese and International cuisine. Dairy-free, vegan and gluten-free options can also be requested. Popular points of interest near the hotel include White Villa, Express Ship Harbour and Lam Son Stadium. The nearest airport is Vung Tau Airport, 3.1 miles from Fusion Suites Vung Tau.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/cDS3JxUBx9kAFLZGQO2m.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/SWdCL6h7nd748bAlYjhs.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:44:57', '2024-01-16 08:47:26', 0, 'fusion-suites-vung-tau', NULL, 'Located in Vung Tau, a 5-minute walk from Front Beach, Fusion Suites Vung Tau provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers room service, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi. Certain rooms at the property include a balcony with a city view.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3925.003304345138!2d107.0732848749265!3d10.341619989781947!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31756f119ff08151%3A0xa02b59fed0425cda!2sFusion%20Suites%20V%C5%A9