(30, 'Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort', 'Lot D14B, Nguyễn Tất Thành, st, Cam Lâm, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 0, '02583996888', NULL, 'https://www.wyndhamhotels.com/wyndham-garden/cam-ranh-vietnam/wyndham-garden-cam-ranh-resort/overview', '<p>Located in Cam Ranh, a 11-minute walk from Bai Dai Beach, Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. With free WiFi, this 5-star hotel offers a kids\' club and room service. The hotel provides garden views, a terrace and a 24-hour front desk. All rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kitchen, a dining area, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. The rooms are equipped with an electric tea pot, while some rooms also feature a balcony and others also feature sea views. At Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort the rooms come with bed linen and towels. At the accommodation you\'ll find a restaurant serving Korean, Seafood and Vietnamese cuisine. Vegetarian, dairy-free and vegan options can also be requested. You can play darts at Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort. There\'s an in-house bar and guests can also use the business area. 100 Egg Mud Bath is 16 miles from the hotel, while Alexandre Yersin Museum is 21 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 2.5 miles from Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/RpPBj05zK6Hx5Gg0gO2m.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/nKFMhztaDrBKZ6NtLXHr.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:47:13', '2024-01-16 08:47:13', 1, 'wyndham-garden-cam-ranh-resort', NULL, 'Located in Cam Ranh, a 11-minute walk from Bai Dai Beach, Wyndham Garden Cam Ranh Resort has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. With free WiFi, this 5-star hotel offers a kids\' club and room service. The hotel provides garden views, a terrace 