(32, 'Fusion Resort Cam Ranh', 'LotD10B, Nguyễn Tất Thành Street, Bãi Đông, Cam Hải Đông, Cam Lâm, Cam Lâm, Khánh Hòa 000000, Vietnam', 0, '02583989777', NULL, 'http://camranh.fusionresorts.com/?partner=6459utm_source=google&utm_medium=organic&utm_campaign=MyBusiness&utm', '<p>Boasting a private beach area, Fusion Resort Cam Ranh offers tranquil and comfortable accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. Guests at Fusion Resort Cam Ranh can indulge in complimentary spa treatments, all-day breakfast and shuttle bus service from/to Nha Trang City. Complimentary classes of Yoga and mediation are available. Enjoying pool and sea views, spacious villas are stylishly furnished with a wardrobe, a flat-screen TV, personal safe and sofa seating area. Electric kettle and mini-bar are also included. The private bathroom comes equipped with a hanging bathtub, hairdryer and free toiletries. Turn down service is available. At Fusion Resort Cam Ranh, you may enjoy a dip in the outdoor pool, have a workout session in the fitness center, or relax in lush green gardens. The 24-hour front desk staff can assist guests with currency exchange, luggage storage, ticketing and laundry services. The property is 8.3 mi from Institute of Oceanography. Cam Ranh Airport is 3.1 mi away. Airport transfers can be arrange upon request at a surcharge. Free parking can be arranged upon request. Fresh, a poolside restaurant, serves authentic Vietnamese dishes, international favorites and fresh seafood.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/exCCvvS99EzdFdjXV2Xt.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Vyc4Exb4ehCv4vyd4pFx.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:49:11', '2024-01-16 08:49:11', 1, 'fusion-resort-cam-ranh', NULL, 'Boasting a private beach area, Fusion Resort Cam Ranh offers tranquil and comfortable accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. Guests at Fusion Resort Cam Ranh can indulge in complimentary spa treatments, all-day breakfast and shuttle bus service from/to Nha Trang City. Complim