(33, 'Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh', 'D12 Slot A, Nguyen Tat Thanh, Ward, Street, Cam Lâm, Khánh Hòa, Vietnam', 0, '02583993666', NULL, 'https://www.radissonhotels.com/en-us/hotels/radisson-blu-resort-cam-ranh?cid=a:se+b:gmb+c:apac+i:local+e:rdb+d:seap+h:VNCAMRST', '<p>Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh features a restaurant, free bikes, a bar and garden in Cam Ranh. With free WiFi, this 5-star resort offers room service and a kids\' club. The resort has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, evening entertainment and a 24-hour front desk. All rooms are fitted with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kettle, a shower, a hairdryer and a wardrobe. With a private bathroom fitted with a bath and free toiletries, rooms at the resort also feature a sea view. At Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh the rooms include a seating area. Guests at the accommodations can enjoy a buffet breakfast. Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh offers 5-star accommodations with a hammam and children\'s playground. You can play tennis at the resort, and the area is popular for cycling. Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh also provides a business center and free private parking. Nha Trang is 20 mi from the accommodations. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International, 4.3 mi from Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/roBgXDn4GB5gC5GNhBZf.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/vP7tJ50u3Rapw6lLy8ke.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:51:11', '2024-01-16 08:51:11', 1, 'radisson-blu-resort-cam-ranh', NULL, 'Radisson Blu Resort Cam Ranh features a restaurant, free bikes, a bar and garden in Cam Ranh. With free WiFi, this 5-star resort offers room service and a kids\' club. The resort has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, evening entertainment and a 24-hour front desk.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3901.944815482368!2d109.20415407495261!3d12.0473179881895!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3