(34, 'Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach', '19 Lac Long Quan Street, Cam An Ward, Hoian City Quang Nam Province, Vietnam, Cẩm An, Hội An, Việt Nam', 4, '02353751888', NULL, 'https://www.wyndhamhotels.com/en-uk/wyndham-garden/hoi-an-vietnam/wyndham-garden-hoi-an-cua-dai/overview', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"THHSODPNGZfSeUePXIYEZFeSTUNQcfAHHaNWe:1 \">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">Bạn đủ điều kiện nhận giảm gi&aacute; Genius tại Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach! Để tiết kiệm tại chỗ nghỉ n&agrave;y, bạn chỉ cần&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?aid=357028&amp;dt=1705394981&amp;response_type=sso&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;state=UooCXk7utcQPMgA4wiaGVVohhmEFSuaW1V1H-j5DnnxR2E5FOivftaQbnLhVz_Nsnpiz8kxBf-bm0tXDGEUGu2OEMyrgeDfHcrVjr6TPcL3LJrYVd3h8M1Dp7k7wVxM9bw4mDPU0bBOKZn6c1tSFaJzhjVDdJ4k2hIwwJaPhQpGw-G6v8N9GXjbc2yM8LWvLdLlG-E75l83PcA1jMn9QYtdUgU0G3PZVA9GAhuYN7JuxG_J5eKOgrfd4MaK3XfmiIGIyCDPYyjBaEZv05tTgbN-6R7rCjy_GubqpjUXh4NJC3NXH6a1utJnJRBd0sRopKAD_r8n20VoLeVXY3h_cuucQrDqEpxbL1SKtuJs&amp;lang=vi&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">đăng nhập.</a></p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Tọa lạc tại th&agrave;nh phố Hội An, Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach cung cấp ph&ograve;ng nghỉ hiện đại v&agrave; c&oacute; khu vực b&atilde;i biển ri&ecirc;ng. Kh&aacute;ch sạn n&agrave;y c&oacute; hồ bơi ngo&agrave;i trời, s&acirc;n hi&ecirc;n cũng như quầy bar v&agrave; nh&agrave; h&agrave;ng trong khu&ocirc;n vi&ecirc;n. Chỗ nghỉ cung cấp WiFi miễn ph&iacute; ở tất cả c&aacute;c khu vực. Tất cả ph&ograve;ng nghỉ tại đ&acirc;y đều được trang bị m&aacute;y điều ho&agrave; v&agrave; TV truyền h&igrave;nh c&aacute;p m&agrave;n h&igrave;nh phẳng. Giường được bố tr&iacute; nệm l&ograve; xo cao cấp với chăn l&ocirc;ng vũ loại 250 sợi vải. Một số ph&ograve;ng c&oacute; khu vực ghế ngồi v&agrave;/hoặc tầm nh&igrave;n ra quang cảnh biển, hồ bơi, khu vườn hoặc th&agrave;nh phố. Ph&ograve;ng tắm ri&ecirc;ng trong mỗi ph&ograve;ng đi k&egrave;m bồn tắm. Dép đi trong phòng, đồ vệ sinh c&aacute; nh&acirc;n miễn ph&iacute; v&agrave; &aacute;o cho&agrave;ng tắm cũng được cung cấp để tạo thuận tiện cho kh&aacute;ch. Nh&acirc;n vi&ecirc;n giao tiếp th&ocirc;ng thạo tiếng Anh, tiếng T&acirc;y Ban Nha, tiếng H&agrave;n, tiếng Nhật v&agrave; tiếng Việt tại quầy lễ t&acirc;n 24 giờ c&oacute; thể hỗ trợ kh&aacute;ch với c&aacute;c dịch vụ nhận ph&ograve;ng/trả ph&ograve;ng cấp tốc v&agrave; ri&ecirc;ng tư, giữ h&agrave;nh l&yacute; c&ugrave;ng c&aacute;c dịch vụ tiền sảnh kh&aacute;c. C&aacute;c chuyến đi trong ng&agrave;y v&agrave; dịch vụ đặt v&eacute; c&oacute; thể được thu xếp tại b&agrave;n đặt tour. Chỗ nghỉ c&oacute; cửa h&agrave;ng qu&agrave; tặng, ph&ograve;ng họp v&agrave; c&aacute;c tiện nghi phục vụ văn ph&ograve;ng kh&aacute;c. Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach cung cấp xe đạp cho kh&aacute;ch sử dụng miễn ph&iacute; v&agrave; dịch vụ đưa đ&oacute;n đến Phố Cổ Hội An. Chỗ nghỉ nằm c&aacute;ch Hội qu&aacute;n Triều Ch&acirc;u 15 ph&uacute;t l&aacute;i xe trong khi s&acirc;n bay quốc tế Đ&agrave; Nẵng c&aacute;ch đ&oacute; 40 ph&uacute;t l&aacute;i xe.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">C&aacute;c cặp đ&ocirc;i đặc biệt th&iacute;ch địa điểm n&agrave;y &mdash; họ cho điểm&nbsp;<strong>8,2</strong>&nbsp;cho kỳ nghỉ d&agrave;nh cho 2 người.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/dagV0gQnkJdP0iqkvM57.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/JUAX7cuN8RxSD8f9cGte.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 08:52:53', '2024-01-16 08:52:53', 1, 'wyndham-garden-hoi-an-cua-dai-beach', NULL, 'Tọa lạc tại thành phố Hội An, Wyndham Garden Hoi An Cua Dai Beach cung cấp phòng nghỉ hiện đại và có khu vực bãi biển riêng. Khách sạn này có hồ bơi ngoài trời, sân hiên cũng như quầy bar và nhà hàng trong khuôn viên. Chỗ nghỉ cung cấp WiFi miễn phí ở tất cả các khu vực.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3837.201419307277!2d108.35869707414696!3d15.898515284756495!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31420d935b8e5649%3A0x250fcaf967f90f2a!2sWyndham%20Garden%20Hoi%20An!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705395088730!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 1),
(35, 'Havana Nha Trang Hotel', '38 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Khánh Hòa, 650000, Vietnam', 5, '02583889999', NULL, 'https://havanahotel.vn/', '<p>Havana Nha Trang Hotel offers modern accommodations just 5 minutes\' walk from 2/4 Square. The sandy beach is just across the street. An outdoor pool, spa treatments and a fitness center are available. Fitted with free WiFi, all guestrooms are nonsmoking and come with a flat-screen TV. A personal safe and electric kettle are included. The private bathroom has a bathtub and free toiletries. Havana Nha Trang Hotel is 25 mi from Nha Trang Airport. Parking is free, while airport transfers are available at a charge. Both Asian and international dishes are served at Spicy Restaurant. A buffet breakfast is available, or guests can also opt for in-room dining. Day trips and car rentals can be arranged at the tour desk. The hotel also provides a business center, babysitting services and a 24-hour front desk.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/RwIi0nVQTng6ltAVTPh7.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/0FKLbZIlCoP57U8rV8U6.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:53:08', '2024-01-16 08:53:08', 1, 'havana-nha-trang-hotel', NULL, 'Havana Nha Trang Hotel offers modern accommodations just 5 minutes\' walk from 2/4 Square. The sandy beach is just across the street. An outdoor pool, spa treatments and a fitness center are available.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.0707946496823!2d109.19326247495576!3d12.24348578800894!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31706778fd8c5dff%3A0xd3c343b165958165!2sPremier%20Havana!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395162194!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(36, 'Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel', '9 Biệt Thự, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 4, '02583529555', NULL, 'http://www.libertycentralnhatrang.com/', '<p>Conveniently located, Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel offers luxurious and elegant accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. It features an outdoor pool, sauna, fitness center and meeting/banquet facilities on site. The hotel is just 656 feet from Nha Trang Beach and 984 feet from Vietnam Sailing Center. Nha Trang Airport is approximately 17 mi away. Tastefully furnished, air-conditioned rooms and suites come equipped with a wardrobe, personal safe, a flat-screen cable TV and seating area. Mini-bar and electric kettle are also included. Offering shower facility, the private bathroom has slippers and bathrobes. At Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel, guests can indulge in a pampering massage at the spa, or enjoy a karaoke session on site. Operating a 24-hour front desk, the friendly staff can assist with laundry, airport transfers and concierge services. The in-house restaurant serves an appetizing selection of local and Continental dishes. After-meal drinks can be enjoyed at the bar.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/aMRFWDWsfrXz4yaNBuH5.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/tkIqOedf86anRjkUDGPr.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:54:36', '2024-01-16 08:54:36', 1, 'liberty-central-nha-trang-hotel', NULL, 'Conveniently located, Liberty Central Nha Trang Hotel offers luxurious and elegant accommodations with free WiFi access throughout the property. It features an outdoor pool, sauna, fitness center and meeting/banquet facilities on site.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.1867673804118!2d109.19309357495557!3d12.235629988016228!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3170677b4bda091b%3A0xdd08e93dd8cf8989!2sLiberty%20Central%20Nha%20Trang!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395254254!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(37, 'Silkotel Hoi An', '14 Hung Vuong Street, Cam Pho, Hoi An, Vietnam', 4, '02353963399', NULL, 'https://hoian.silkotel.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at Silkotel Hoi An! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?aid=357028&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;state=UoUCXk7utcQPMgBkI6CB7XjvAXO7fGm7_ROlRWoThAipplGdeL9QWIm2Jm3a64GEA_4Ked5d_nMoGNDw69Q6TNBvVdZeF4_cdNpn2KzOiw5FPV6NS1Uy_Q_2GYsp48qiVVWMm3lgls8N1y_lljzrqDzHaUaabJmZws8piL-RSY_Ixf0W7keAjVi9nTXHgPiDF4USe2PPYpVJC5C5m5VrVn1SzU9XwS7ORUP8dQQFgFQWjpRY9NChdMTnzgR_3Tlq3pb5A9qkEXVfx7dKRCoInPfQG-bvIdmbuyzMDoDAdkQ3wdN4-3zrqo088SHTej3ohu7q_wZVC6noZpM30vzh9HvkzxrGXU22&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;lang=en-gb&amp;response_type=sso&amp;dt=1705395215\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in the heart of tranquil Hoi An, Silkotel Hoi An offers relaxing accommodation in Hoi An. It features a spa and fitness centre, swimming pool and an on-site restaurant that offers both local and international delights. Massage services are available at additional charges. Free WiFi is available throughout the property. The air-conditioned rooms at Silkotel Hoi An all come with a TV, separate seating area, safety deposit box and electric kettle. The en suite bathroom is fitted with either bath or shower facilities, hairdryer, slippers, bathrobes and free toiletries. At the property you will also find a sun terrace, barbecue facilities, a tour desk, luggage storage and laundry facilities. Guests who wish to explore the area can rent bicycles to explore. Guests travelling on business can make use of the on-site meeting room facilities and fax/photocopying services. The property operates a 24-hour front desk. Free parking is available on-site. Japanese Covered Bridge is 500 metres from Silkotel Hoi An, while Thanh Ha Village is approximately 2 km away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, which is 22 km away.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.5</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/cxTPtyrLZ96BcVHSv6x5.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/T88sgSkLpBNSrltmaSX1.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 08:55:25', '2024-01-16 08:55:25', 1, 'silkotel-hoi-an', NULL, 'Located in the heart of tranquil Hoi An, Silkotel Hoi An offers relaxing accommodation in Hoi An. It features a spa and fitness centre, swimming pool and an on-site restaurant that offers both local and international delights. Massage services are available at additional charges. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3837.564672503176!2d108.31977457414652!3d15.87946128477288!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31420e7c95d29c35%3A0xe1b303bfe9f6dc2d!2sSilkotel%20Hoi%20An!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705395298415!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 1),
(38, 'InterContinental Nha Trang, an IHG Hotel', '32-34 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 300202, Vietnam', 5, '02583887777', NULL, 'https://www.ihg.com/intercontinental/hotels/us/en/nha-trang/nhach/hoteldetail?cm_mmc=GoogleMaps-_-IC-_-VN-_-NHACH', '<p>The latest addition to the InterContinental family in Vietnam is InterContinental Nha Trang, located in the Nha Trang City\'s popular Tran Phu Street. The hotel provides complimentary WiFi access in all areas of the property. Elegantly furnished with earth-tone d&eacute;cor and wooden furnishings, the luxurious air-conditioned rooms and suites include a balcony, seating area, mini-bar and a flat-screen TV with satellite channels. En suite marble bathroom comes with a bathtub, separate shower and bathrobes. Complimentary tea/coffee making facilities are also provided daily. InterContinental Nha Trang offers a myriad of facilities and amenities for guests to enjoy. At Cookbook Caf&eacute;, guests are able to tantalize their tastebuds with all-day dining a-la-carte menus, evening buffets and even candle-lit dinners with a variety of local seafood. Spa InterContinental offers modern and traditional treatments, while the fitness center comes equipped with 3 outdoor pools. Alternatively, guests may enjoy cocktails at either the Lobby Bar or the Aqualine Bar. InterContinental Nha Trang is 0.6 mi away from the Nha Trang beach area, 1.2 mi away from the Nha Trang Train Station, and 17 mi away from the Nha Trang Airport.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/VudNzMNGARk134VzwIiW.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/tnWsJgxGTruxm596G5DV.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:57:22', '2024-01-16 08:57:22', 1, 'intercontinental-nha-trang-an-ihg-hotel', NULL, 'The latest addition to the InterContinental family in Vietnam is InterContinental Nha Trang, located in the Nha Trang City\'s popular Tran Phu Street. The hotel provides complimentary WiFi access in all areas of the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899