(40, 'Imperial Nha Trang', '20 Trần Phú, Vĩnh Hoà, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 4, '02583736688', NULL, 'http://www.imperialnhatranghotel.com/', '<p>Located in Nha Trang, a 3-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach, Imperial Nha Trang has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. Offering a restaurant, the property also has a bar, as well as a sauna. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At Imperial Nha Trang rooms have bed linen and towels. Institute of Oceanography is 1.2 miles from the accommodation, while Alexandre Yersin Museum is 1.2 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 20 miles from Imperial Nha Trang.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/tbYqjsve9mY8AjIclcxY.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/sat16j9jTeyUZ2reUVZF.png\"]', '2024-01-16 08:59:07', '2024-01-16 08:59:07', 1, 'imperial-nha-trang', NULL, 'Located in Nha Trang, a 3-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach, Imperial Nha Trang has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. Offering a restaurant, the property also has a bar, as well as a sauna. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.4229957562834!2d109.20147587495529!3d12.219612888030895!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31706743be0c3c9b%3A0x5bd407f53fb85978!2sImperial%20Nha%20Trang%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395516706!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgra