(41, 'Venue Hotel', '24 Tôn Đản, Phường Lộc Thọ, Khánh Hòa, Vietnam', 3, '02586258888', NULL, 'https://rutgon.me/mop4LK', '<p>Located across the road from Tran Phu Beach in Nha Trang, Venue Hotel Nha Trang offers well-appointed, elegant accommodations just 984 feet from 2/4 Square. Guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant, or a drink of their choice at the in-house bar. Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the property. Bathed in sunlight in the day, each warmly-decorated room is air conditioned and is fitted with large windows that offer views of the sea, city or the surrounding streets. The rooms come with a TV, mini-bar, safety deposit box and an electric kettle. All rooms come with an private bathroom with complimentary toiletries. Guests driving to the property can benefit from the complimentary parking on-site. Well-versed in a few languages, staff at the property are available 24 hours a day at the front desk to assist you with inquiries. Luggage storage, currency exchange and a tour desk are available at the property. Guests may also rent a bicycle or car at the property. Cam Ranh International Airport is 16 mi from the property.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/PjyGPspkk2zbottq4AdM.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/DAv6GlOoa1DG0LqHUrzR.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:00:56', '2024-01-16 09:00:56', 1, 'venue-hotel', NULL, 'Located across the road from Tran Phu Beach in Nha Trang, Venue Hotel Nha Trang offers well-appointed, elegant accommodations just 984 feet from 2/4 Square. Guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant, or a drink of their choice at the in-house bar. Complimentary WiFi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.1606733385925!2d109.19360717495573!3d12.237397988014534!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3170677b06007567%3A0x15a6b5517f38f10e!2sVenue%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395628273!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"