(42, 'Gem Riverside Hotel Hoi An', 'Lương Như Bích 4, Cam Nam, Hoi An, Vietnam', 4, '02352207777', NULL, 'http://gemriversidehoian.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Set in Hoi An, 800 metres from Assembly Hall of Chaozhou Chinese Congregation, Gem Riverside Hotel Hoi An offers accommodation with free bikes, free private parking, an outdoor swimming pool and a garden. Boasting room service, this property also welcomes guests with a restaurant and a terrace. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, a shared lounge and free WiFi throughout the property. All guest rooms come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a fridge, a kettle, a shower, free toiletries and a desk. The rooms are equipped with a safety deposit box, while some rooms also feature a balcony and others also feature city views. At the hotel all rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels. Breakfast is available every morning, and includes buffet, &agrave; la carte and continental options. Guests at Gem Riverside Hotel Hoi An will be able to enjoy activities in and around Hoi An, like cycling. Hoi An Historic Museum is 1.4 km from the accommodation, while Japanese Covered Bridge is 1.5 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 31 km from Gem Riverside Hotel Hoi An.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/BFm3zePhYCPvA0AbLO5O.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Uq4Z6hkXYNSft6N2VR6e.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:01:01', '2024-01-16 09:01:01', 1, 'gem-riverside-hotel-hoi-an', NULL,