(43, 'The Empyrean Nha Trang', '2 Nguyễn Thị Minh Khai, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 57100, Vietnam', 5, '02583848888', NULL, 'http://theempyreanhotel.com/', '<p>Located in Nha Trang, a 10-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach, The Empyrean Nha Trang provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a restaurant. With a bar, the 5-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The property has room service, a 24-hour front desk and luggage storage for guests. At the hotel, each room has a desk. Every room includes an electric tea pot, a flat-screen TV and a safety deposit box, while certain rooms will provide you with a balcony and some have city views. All guest rooms feature a closet. Popular points of interest near The Empyrean Nha Trang include Nha Trang Centre Shopping Mall, Nha Trang Catheral and Tram Huong Tower. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International, 22 miles from the accommodation, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/6oSCadVgZ3HKo4S7yWeE.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/HnINUATxP4k287yWO8LJ.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:02:38', '2024-01-16 09:02:38', 1, 'the-empyrean-nha-trang', NULL, 'Located in Nha Trang, a 10-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach, The Empyrean Nha Trang provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a restaurant. With a bar, the 5-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The property has room service, a 24-hour front desk and luggage storage for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.1403268561394!2d109.19304857495567!3d12.238776388013267!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31706742888ef709%3A0x87558e9dce4ef061!2sThe%20Empyrean%20Nha%20Trang!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705395735809!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"