(49, 'Bel Marina Hoi An Resort', '127 Nguyen Phuc Tan, Cam Pho Ward, Hoi An, Cam Pho, Hoi An, Vietnam', 4, '02353938888', NULL, 'https://belmarinahoian.com/en/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Bel Marina Hoi An Resort is within a convenient 7-minute walk from Hoi An Ancient Town, a UNESCO World Heritage Site. It features a spa and wellness centre, while free Wi-Fi access is available in the entire resort. Fitted with parquet flooring, air-conditioned villas are equipped with a personal safe, a flat-screen cable TV and minibar. A wardrobe and seating area are also included. En suite bathrooms come with a hairdryer, bathtub, shower facilities and free toiletries. Operating a 24-hour front desk and security, Bel Marina Hoi An Resort provides luggage storage, laundry and car rental services. The tour desk can assist with bookings of tour excursions and travel arrangements. Accompanied with beautiful views of the river, the in-house Marine Restaurant serves Vietnamese and international cuisines in a buffet style. 24-hour room service is available. The resort is approximately 4 km to An Bang Beach, while Da Nang International Airport can be reached within 30 km away. Airport transfer can also be arranged at an additional charge.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.6</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/AWFda859xw9RoLnLz2az.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/4LGy6A9lP8VPS9UzLKGy.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:09:46', '2024-01-16 09:09:46', 1, 'bel-marina-hoi-an-resort', NULL, 'Bel Marina Hoi An Resort is within a convenient 7-minute walk from Hoi An Ancient Town, a U