(58, 'Queen Ann Nha Trang Hotel', '100 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 5, '02583597888', NULL, 'http://www.queenannnhatrang.com/', '<p>Queen Ann Nha Trang Hotel offers accommodations Nha Trang, 2625 feet from Sailing Center Vietnam. It features an outdoor swimming pool and guests can enjoy meals at the in-house restaurant or have drink at the bar. Free WiFi is available throughout the property. It is 2953 feet to Nha Trang Night Market while Nha Trang Beach is 0.6 mi away. Long Son Pagoda and Nha Trang Bay Tourism Pier are 2.5 mi from Queen Ann Nha Trang Hotel and Ponagar Tower is 3 mi away. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 15 mi from the property. Airport transfers are available at additional charges. A flat-screen TV with cable channels, as well as an iPod docking station are available. You will find a kettle in the room. The rooms come with a private bathroom. For your comfort, you will find bathrobes, slippers and free toiletries. Guests can approach the 24-hour front desk for luggage storage. A free fitness center is available for guests to work out. Alternatively, guests can indulge in a massage treatment at the spa center or get free access to the swimming pool. Royal Restaurant offers a selection of local and international cuisine, while the Lobby Lounge serves up light refreshments. Guests receive free welcome drink and fruits on the check-in day.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/ZSFh1BB45KSfURmmwcDG.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Hukp8KBWdZpqXt8H93ne.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:17:55', '2024-01-16 09:17:55', 1, 'queen-ann-nha-trang-hotel', NULL, 'Queen Ann Nha Trang Hotel offers accommodations Nha Trang, 2625 feet from Sailing Center Vietnam. It features an outdoor swimming pool and guests can enjoy meals at the in-house restaurant or have drink at the bar. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.3243298831762!2d109.19758087495548!3d12.226305288024758!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3170676621445443%3A0xa459153630f9f44d!2sQueen%20Ann%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705396653769!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(59, 'Nha Trang Lodge Hotel', '42 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 4, '02583521500', NULL, 'http://www.nhatranglodgehotel.com/', '<p>Nha Trang Lodge Hotel is located along Nha Trang Beach, 164 feet from 2/4 Square. It features rooms with free internet access and some with seafront balconies. A spa, pool and casino are available. Nha Trang Lodge is a 5-minute drive from Nha Trang Railway Station. Phu Dong Water Park is 0.7 mi away. Rooms are fully carpeted and come with a flat-screen TV offering cable channels. Each has a balcony and seating area. A mini-bar and bathroom toiletries are provided. Guests can relax with a massage or sauna session or head to the disco for some dancing. Currency exchange and car rental services are available at the tour desk. A souvenir shop and business center are offered. European and Asian cuisine can be enjoyed at Nha Trang Lodge Restaurant. Local Vietnamese dishes and seafood is also served.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/Dj2yGJDHspcJdCh11IAQ.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/uJ92slvQE0ZPTb4S5EBd.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:19:49', '2024-01-16 09:19:49', 1, 'nha-trang-lodge-hotel', NULL, 'Nha Trang Lodge Hotel is located along Nha Trang Beach, 164 feet from 2/4 Square. It features rooms with free internet access and some with seafront balconies. A spa, pool and casino are available.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.0970638931726!2d109.19357677495574!3d12.241706788010644!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317067796e11dacf%3A0x1946b224b9b3948f!2sNha%20Trang%20Lodge%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705396765029!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(60, 'Fivitel Hoi An Hotel', 'Âu Cơ, Cua Dai, Hoi An, Vietnam', 4, '02356254545', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/Fivitel.HoiAn.Hotel', '<p>Facing the beachfront, Fivitel Hoi An Hotel offers 4-star accommodation in Hoi An and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and fitness centre. Among the various facilities are a garden, a terrace, as well as a bar. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, a shared lounge and free WiFi throughout the property. Guest rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. All rooms are equipped with a kettle, while selected rooms are equipped with a patio and others also offer sea views. At Fivitel Hoi An Hotel each room is fitted with bed linen and towels. A buffet, &agrave; la carte or continental breakfast is available daily at the property. At the accommodation you will find a restaurant serving American, Vietnamese and local cuisine. Vegetarian, vegan and gluten-free options can also be requested. The area is popular for cycling, and car hire is available at Fivitel Hoi An Hotel. Guests can make use of the business centre or relax in the snack bar. Cua Dai Beach is 600 metres from the hotel, while An Bang Beach is 2.7 km away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 27 km from Fivitel Hoi An Hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/zr7kULq4AO2Dg5cxymee.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/dZlUVW669VZ04niB7ZX0.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:20:55', '2024-01-16 09:20:55', 1, 'fivitel-hoi-an-hotel', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Fivitel Hoi An Hotel offers 4-star accommodation in Hoi An and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and fitness centre. Among the various facilities are a garden, a terrace, as well as a bar. The accommodation provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, a shared lounge and free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"ht