(61, 'Majestic Premium Hotel', '96b5 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 3, '02583878899', NULL, 'http://www.majesticnhatranghotel.com/', '<p>Majestic Premium Hotel has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, a garden and shared lounge in Nha Trang. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property has a concierge service, a tour desk and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a TV and a private bathroom with a shower. At Majestic Premium Hotel all rooms include bed linen and towels. A buffet breakfast is available every morning at the accommodation. Nha Trang Beach is a 12-minute walk from Majestic Premium Hotel, while Tram Huong Tower is 1.1 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 21 miles from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/PWzrULgw9VwNMnFvRkqI.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/HuIdyPmqNg4Z4wN9Niqe.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:23:57', '2024-01-16 09:23:57', 1, 'majestic-premium-hotel', NULL, 'Majestic Premium Hotel has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, a garden and shared lounge in Nha Trang. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property has a concierge service, a tour desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.305676993592!2d109.19701297495554!3d12.227570088023638!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31706782769ddcf5%3A0xf636d922cfcdbe92!2sMajestic%20Premium%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397000874!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(62, 'Nostalgia Hotel and Spa', '103A Hung Vuong, Thanh Ha Ward, Cam Pho, Hoi An, Vietnam', 3, '0905153142', NULL, 'http://hoiannostalgiahotel.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Offering a refreshing outdoor pool and a spa centre, Nostalgia Hotel and Spa is situated just 900 metres from Japanese Covered Bridge in Hoi An. The hotel features a sun terrace where guests can relax, and a bar where guests can choose to indulge on their choice of drink. Each room at this hotel is air conditioned and is equipped with a TV. A kettle is available for coffee/tea making. Some units have a seating area. Rooms come with a private bathroom that have a bath or shower. For your comfort, you will find bath robes and slippers. Nostalgia Hotel and Spa offers free WiFi throughout the property. There is a 24-hour front desk, gift shop, and shops at the property. Bike hire is available at this hotel and the area is popular for cycling. The hotel also offers car hire. Assembly Hall of the Cantonese Chinese Congregation is 1 km from Nostalgia Hotel and Spa, while Hoi An Ancient Town is 1.2 km away. Da Nang International Airport is a 45-minute taxi ride from the property. It takes 40 minutes from Danang Train Station by taxi to reach the hotel.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.6</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/tWj67EUPgQScolfJbDIr.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Ofjsu6BqaneKZlwPzWGo.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:24:28', '2024-01-16 09:24:28', 1, 'nostalgia-hotel-and-spa', NULL, 'Offering a refreshing outdoor pool and a spa centre, Nostalgia Hotel and Spa is situated just 900 metres from Japanese Covered Bridge in Hoi An. The hotel features a sun terrace where guests can relax, and a bar where guests can choose to indulge on their choice of drink.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3837.5563632611425!2d108.31629617414644!3d15.87989738477248!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31420e6365b59d39%3A0x325c8b2bd6725268!2sHoian%20Nostalgia%20Hotel%20%26%20Spa!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397021438!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 1),
(63, 'Vesna Hotel', '100 Trần Phú, Lộc Thọ, Nha Trang, Khánh Hòa 650000, Vietnam', 5, '02583885858', NULL, 'https://vesnahotelnhatrang.com/', '<p>Facing the beachfront, Vesna Hotel offers 5-star accommodations in Nha Trang and has a fitness center, shared lounge and restaurant. A 12-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach and 1.2 miles from Tram Huong Tower, the property provides a bar and a private beach area. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a kids\' club and free WiFi throughout the property. All rooms come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, an electric tea pot, a shower, free toiletries and a desk. A buffet, continental or American breakfast is served at the property. The hotel offers a range of wellness facilities including an indoor pool and a hot tub. Guests at Vesna Hotel will be able to enjoy activities in and around Nha Trang, like cycling. Institute of Oceanography is 1.7 miles from the accommodation, while Alexandre Yersin Museum is 1.7 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 21 miles from Vesna Hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/Yee93EYE3ELPMnZGEDl2.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/NVCSdxjhhUrXvNCXJj5t.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:26:02', '2024-01-16 09:26:02', 1, 'vesna-hotel', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Vesna Hotel offers 5-star accommodations in Nha Trang and has a fitness center, shared lounge and restaurant. A 12-minute walk from Nha Trang Beach and 1.2 miles from Tram Huong Tower, the property provides a bar and a private beach area. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a kids\' club and free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3899.331543947883!2d109.19794717495552!3d12.225816088025207!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317067e4d806e3d5%3A0xdfeaf8e440b530eb!2sVesna%20Hotel%20Nha%20Trang!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397138486!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 7),
(64, 'InterContinental Đà Nẵng Sun Peninsula Resort', 'Bai Sac, Son Tra Peninsula, Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363938888', NULL, 'Bai Sac, Son Tra Peninsula, Danang, Vietnam', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience World-class Service at InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort, an IHG Hotel</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Boasting several fine dining options like the acclaimed La Maison 1888, InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort provides a luxurious retreat with private beach, a 2 large outdoor swimming pools and a spa. Spectacular views of the ocean can be enjoyed from the resort. All accommodations are luxuriously decorated and provide private balconies. The resort&rsquo;s beachfront villas are nestled within spectacular boulders at the foot of the mountain and come with private pools, a sundeck and luxurious bathroom facilities. Select rooms have a spa bath and a private dining pavilion offering magnificent ocean views. It takes 45 minutes from the hotel to Danang Airport and 30 minutes to Ngu Hanh Son. Cham Museum is about 16 mi away, while The Imperial City of Huế, The Old Town of Hội An and the Mỹ Sơn ruins, popular UNESCO World Heritage sites are about 28 mi from the hotel. Visit the world-acclaimed Bana Hills Golf Club or challenge yourself at the Danang Golf Club. The resort&rsquo;s many recreational options include cycling, yoga and hiking. Alternatively, guests can request for pampering massage and body treatments at the spa. There is also a modern fitness center on site. Enjoy fresh Vietnamese delicacies in private booths, 328 feet above sea level at Citron Restaurant. For a relaxed beachfront dining experience, visit Barefoot and sample delicious grilled meats and fresh seafood paired with cocktails and wines. Buffalo Bar serves vintage champagne and premium hand-rolled cigars.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/vWGDHRbFpTVbTzjpwhdb.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/u3BYFmem3YfM0UVPJCWZ.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:29:33', '2024-01-16 09:29:33', 1, 'intercontinental-da-nang-sun-peninsula-resort', NULL, 'Boasting several fine dining options like the acclaimed La Maison 1888, InterContinental Danang Sun Peninsula Resort provides a luxurious retreat with private beach, a 2 large outdoor swimming pools and a spa. Spectacular views of the ocean can be enjoyed from the resort.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3832.900168159531!2d108.3027337741528!3d16.122464384564765!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31423d9513ec9199%3A0x5ade8a2bd4daad0d!2sInterContinental%20%C4%90%C3%A0%20N%E1%BA%B5ng%20Sun%20Peninsula%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397318502!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(65, 'Mövenpick Resort Phan Thiet', 'V24W+2CF, Tiến Thành, Thành phố Phan Thiết, Bình Thuận, Vietnam', 0, NULL, NULL, 'https://www.movenpickresortphanthiet.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Facing the beachfront, M&ouml;venpick Resort Phan Thiet offers 5-star accommodations in Phan Thiet and has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center and garden. Featuring a kids\' club, this property also welcomes guests with a restaurant and a terrace. The property has evening entertainment and room service. The resort will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a private bathroom with a bidet. All rooms feature a closet. Breakfast is available every morning, and includes buffet, continental and Asian options. M&ouml;venpick Resort Phan Thiet has a playground. You can play pool at the accommodation. Staff at the 24-hour front desk speak English, Vietnamese and Chinese. Tien Thanh Beach is a 3-minute walk from M&ouml;venpick Resort Phan Thiet, while Phan Thiet Train Station is 8 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Vung Tau Airport, 89 miles from the resort.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'hotels/January2024/QiiGaFdkTNs1iYSqcylI.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/yWDCT9wBMaTFCc8Qi3MH.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:30:14', '2024-01-16 09:30:14', 1, 'movenpick-resort-phan-thiet', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Mövenpick Resort Phan Thiet offers 5-star accommodations in Phan Thiet and has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center and garden. Featuring a kids\' club, this property also welcomes guests with a restaurant and a terrace. The property has evening entertainment and room service.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3918.4275149997943!2d108.04346697493393!3d10.855052389298535!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31742b0010c8a251%3A0x292baa3fa5cf441d!2sM%C3%B6venpick%20Resort%20Phan%20Thi%E1%BA%BFt!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397387622!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 8),
(66, 'Radisson Resort Phan Thiet', 'Tien Hoa Hamlet, Lạc Long Quân, Street, Tp. Phan Thiết, Bình Thuận 77000, Vietnam', 0, '02522248888', NULL, 'https://www.radissonhotels.com/en-us/hotels/radisson-resort-phan-thiet?cid=a:se+b:gmb+c:apac+i:local+e:rad+d:seap+h:VNPHHRST', '<p>Located in Phan Thiet, 8.7 miles from Phan Thiet Train Station, Radisson Resort Phan Thiet provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. With free WiFi, this 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. Guests can have a drink at the bar. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a shower. All guest rooms include a closet. The daily breakfast offers buffet, continental or Asian options. At Radisson Resort Phan Thiet you\'ll find a restaurant serving American, Austrian and Asian cuisine. Vegetarian and vegan options can also be requested. The accommodation has a terrace. Binh Thuan Bus Station is 9.4 miles from Radisson Resort Phan Thiet, while Sea Link Golf Course is 10 miles away. The nearest airport is Vung Tau Airport, 88 miles from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/0EGtHAnsTNz4y2TCl2S4.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/pqCkHNll47sZiILQJWMn.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:31:46', '2024-01-16 09:31:46', 1, 'radisson-resort-phan-thiet', NULL, 'Located in Phan Thiet, 8.7 miles from Phan Thiet Train Station, Radisson Resort Phan Thiet provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. With free WiFi, this 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. Guests can have a drink at the bar.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3918.563288156779!2d108.03930277493384!3d10.84469428930829!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3176911c8c7fdedf%3A0x477c7a024dae7a3!2sRadisson%20Resort%20Phan%20Thiet!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397482104!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 8),
(67, 'Bay Capital Danang', '17 Quang Trung - Hai Chau - Da Nang, Danang, Vietnam', 1, '02367307999', NULL, 'https://www.baycapitaldanang.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Get the celebrity treatment with world-class service at Bay Capital Danang</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in Danang, 1.8 miles from Thanh Binh Beach, Bay Capital Danang has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. Each room at the 5-star hotel has city views, and guests can enjoy access to a terrace and to a sauna. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property. At the hotel the rooms come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. At Bay Capital Danang each room has bed linen and towels. At the accommodation you\'ll find a restaurant serving American, Chinese and Italian cuisine. Vegetarian, dairy-free and vegan options can also be requested. Bike rental and car rental are available at this hotel and the area is popular for cycling. Popular points of interest near Bay Capital Danang include Indochina Riverside Mall, Song Han Bridge and Cham Museum. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 2.5 miles from the hotel.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.2</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/TUKRtTmfFWBcad8afGAd.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Fs5pD26A7aQ2y1twoVuo.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:32:32', '2024-01-16 09:32:32', 1, 'bay-capital-danang', NULL, 'Located in Danang, 1.8 miles from Thanh Binh Beach, Bay Capital Danang has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. Each room at the 5-star hotel has city views, and guests can enjoy access to a terrace and to a sauna. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.8160859382333!2d108.21920907415154!3d16.075030784605353!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314219c2228221b5%3A0xc72b8c79957fa253!2sBay%20Capital%20Danang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397430084!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(68, 'The Cliff Resort & Residences, Mui Ne', 'Zone 5, Phu Hai, Ward/5 Nguyễn Đình Chiểu, Phú Hài, Thành phố Phan Thiết, Bình Thuận 80000, Vietnam', 0, '19000394', NULL, 'https://www.thecliffresort.com.vn/', '<p>A 2-minute walk from Ong Dia Rock Beach in Mui Ne, The Cliff Residence provides accommodations with access to spa facilities, wellness packages, and beauty services. This beachfront property offers access to pool at the pool table, free private parking, and free Wifi. The apartment offers a pool with a view with a pool bar, as well as a hot tub and a 24-hour front desk. With direct access to a balcony with pool views, the spacious air-conditioned apartment consists of 2 bedrooms. Offering a terrace with sea views, this apartment also has a satellite flat-screen TV, a well-equipped kitchen with a microwave, a fridge, and a stovetop, as well as 1 bathroom with a walk-in shower and bathrobes. The apartment offers bed linen, towels, and daily room service. Guests may eat at the on-site family-friendly restaurant, which is open for dinner, brunch, cocktails, and high tea. Yoga classes and fitness classes are provided at the fitness room on site. You can play table tennis at this 4-star apartment, and the area is popular for canoeing and hiking. Snorkeling and cycling can be enjoyed nearby, while a car rental service and a private beach area are also available on-site. Ham Tien Beach is a 14-minute walk from the apartment, while Sea Link Golf Course is 4.8 miles away. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong, 86 miles from The Cliff Residence, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/thacctPWDykGlJ3nmewq.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/SsdyAFoqCOcsVBHh6KGN.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:33:53', '2024-01-16 09:33:53', 1, 'the-cliff-resort-and-residences-mui-ne', NULL, 'A 2-minute walk from Ong Dia Rock Beach in Mui Ne, The Cliff Residence provides accommodations with access to spa facilities, wellness packages, and beauty services. This beachfront property offers access to pool at the pool table, free private parking, and free Wifi. The apartment offers a pool with a view with a pool bar, as well as a hot tub and a 24-hour front desk.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3917.3466080906583!2d108.17691297493516!3d10.937168789221587!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317684e8a7e756db%3A0x7e8a340fdec624db!2sThe%20Cliff%20Resort%20%26%20Residences%2C%20Mui%20Ne!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397611501!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 8),
(69, 'TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach', '292 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, My An Ward, Ngu Hanh Son District, Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363755999', NULL, 'https://tmshotel.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool, a fitness center and restaurant in Danang. Featuring room service, this property also provides guests with a playground. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a shuttle service, a kids\' club and free WiFi throughout the property. At the hotel all rooms are equipped with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. All rooms come with an electric tea pot, while some rooms come with a kitchen with a fridge, a microwave and a minibar. All guest rooms feature a desk. TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach offers a buffet or continental breakfast. There\'s an on-site bar and guests can also use the business area. My Khe Beach is a few steps from the accommodation, while Bac My An Beach is a 9-minute walk away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 4.3 miles from TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/YovTY3hwlFujkbKMBwoq.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/wLoxUxKYuX0O93UCkwVG.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:35:28', '2024-01-16 09:35:28', 1, 'tms-hotel-da-nang-beach', NULL, 'TMS Hotel Da Nang Beach features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool, a fitness center and restaurant in Danang. Featuring room service, this property also provides guests with a playground. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a shuttle service, a kids\' club and free WiFi throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3834.27618636602!2d108.24571137415087!3d16.051151584625693!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31421725e6dc00a3%3A0x732a2f64f35242ab!2sTMS%20Hotel%20Da%20Nang%20Beach!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397693437!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(70, 'Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa', '20 b Nguyễn Đình Chiểu, Phường Hàm Tiến, Thành phố Phan Thiết, Bình Thuận, Vietnam', 0, '0938235535', NULL, 'http://www.uniquevn.com/', '<p>Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa features an outdoor pool on its private beach and a rooftop restaurant overlooking Muine Bay. It provides spacious air-conditioned rooms with private balconies, free Wi-Fi and buffet breakfast. Featuring sea views and cool breezes, the modern rooms boast over-sized windows and classic wood furnishings. They have a flat-screen satellite TV, tea/coffee maker and a private bathroom. A relaxing massage and beauty treatments can be enjoyed at the spa and hair salon. Other leisure options include a hot tub, steam baths and water sports. The rooftop restaurant offers hearty international menus while the Poolside Restaurant Bar &amp; Lounge serves pizzas and cocktails. Room service is available. Resort Unique Mui Ne is a 20-minute drive from Phan Thiet&acirc; city center and 124 mi from Ho Chi Minh City. It provides charged airport transfers and free parking.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/CITqjjeIfYsfcbbSs0br.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/zJjhSJ1pet34spVtaZ5f.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:35:31', '2024-01-16 09:35:31', 1, 'unique-mui-ne-resort-and-spa', NULL, 'Unique Mui Ne Resort and Spa features an outdoor pool on its private beach and a rooftop restaurant overlooking Muine Bay. It provides spacious air-conditioned rooms with private balconies, free Wi-Fi and buffet breakfast.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3917.2761534353335!2d108.19256207493524!3d10.9425000892165!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31768e4b454337c3%3A0xf2b819ee3b839fa9!2sUnique%20Mui%20Ne%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397713450!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 8),
(71, 'Rosa Alba Resort & Villas Tuy Hoa', '88 Lê Duẩn, Phường 9, Tuy Hòa, Phú Yên, Vietnam', 0, '02572222222', NULL, 'http://rosaalbaresort.com/', '<p>Facing the beachfront, Rosa Alba Resort &amp; Villas Tuy Hoa offers 5-star accommodations in Tuy Hoa and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and fitness center. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared kitchen, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a private bathroom with a shower. Selected rooms include a kitchenette with a stovetop. At Rosa Alba Resort &amp; Villas Tuy Hoa every room is equipped with bed linen and towels. Guests at the accommodation can enjoy a buffet or an Asian breakfast. Rosa Alba Resort &amp; Villas Tuy Hoa has a terrace. Guests at the hotel will be able to enjoy activities in and around Tuy Hoa, like cycling. Guests can use the business center or relax in the bar. Tuy Hoa Beach is a 6-minute walk from Rosa Alba Resort &amp; Villas Tuy Hoa. The nearest airport is Tuy Hoa, 4.3 miles from the accommodation, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/1W5EE48MWWUhA9RAJyeI.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/DHBqwDT8lBPPrl2hhNAn.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:37:19', '2024-01-16 09:37:19', 1, 'rosa-alba-resort-and-villas-tuy-hoa', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Rosa Alba Resort & Villas Tuy Hoa offers 5-star accommodations in Tuy Hoa and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and fitness center. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared kitchen, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3885.833358380686!2d109.30652067497066!3d13.10974108721847!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316fed63c6363e65%3A0x5aa93811b8c4722e!2sRosa%20Alba%20Resort%20-%20Tuy%20Hoa!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705397820955!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 9);
