(72, 'Four Points by Sheraton Danang', '118-120 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, Phuoc My Ward, 550000 Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363997979', NULL, 'https://www.marriott.com/en-us/hotels/dadfp-four-points-by-sheraton-danang/overview/?scid=f2ae0541-1279-4f24-b197-a979c79310b0', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Get the celebrity treatment with world-class service at Four Points by Sheraton Danang</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Four Points by Sheraton Danang is located in Da Nang, in the My Khe Beach district. The property is set 1.2 mi from Song Han Bridge and 1.4 mi from Love Lock Bridge Da Nang. The property is located 1.4 mi from Indochina Riverside Mall. Air-conditioned rooms at Four Points by Sheraton Danang come with a flat screen TV and a balcony overlooking the breathtaking view while some units have a seating area.The private bathrooms come with a hairdryer and free toiletries. Free bottled water can be found in all guestrooms. The hotel serves breakfast and fresh coffee daily. Guests enjoy both local and international dishes at the restaurants. Four Points by Sheraton Danang also features a bar where guests can get unwind and have relaxing moments. There is a swimming pool, as well as a free fitness center at the property. Cham Museum is 1.9 mi from the hotel, while Asia Park Danang is 3.1 mi from the property. Da Nang International Airport is 3.7 mi away.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.7</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/CLOTlyUWBvIKWC028oij.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/e0IRSJjzb9Nm6dZwFbhP.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:38:48', '2024-01-16 09:38:48', 1, 'four-points-by-sheraton-danang', NULL, 'Four Points by Sheraton Danang is located in Da Nang, in the My Khe Beach district. The property is set 1.2 mi from Song Han Bridge and 1.4 mi from Love Lock Bridge Da Nang. The property is located 1.4 mi from Indochina Riverside Mall.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.761313268505!2d108.24282467415162!3d16.077871184602873!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142178ebc260505%3A0xc6eeac18a1830e50!2sFour%20Points%20by%20Sheraton%20Danang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705397890711!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(73, 'Zannier Hotels Bai San Hô', 'Hòa Thạnh, Sông Cầu, Phú Yên, Vietnam', 0, '02573830000', NULL, 'http://www.zannierhotels.com/baisanho/en/', '<p>Facing the beachfront, Zannier Hotels Bai San H&ocirc; offers 5-star accommodations in Song Cau and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and garden. Featuring family rooms, this property also provides guests with a playground. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a closet, a coffee machine, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a terrace and a private bathroom with a bath. The rooms come with an electric tea pot, while some rooms will provide you with a balcony and others also provide guests with sea views. At Zannier Hotels Bai San H&ocirc; every room has bed linen and towels. A buffet breakfast is available daily at the accommodation. At Zannier Hotels Bai San H&ocirc; you\'ll find a restaurant serving Vietnamese, Asian and International cuisine. Vegetarian, dairy-free and vegan options can also be requested. Guests at the hotel will be able to enjoy activities in and around Song Cau, like cycling. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 38 miles from Zannier Hotels Bai San H&ocirc;.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/WNlgMKsOQwGFnLRWdooQ.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/NNufaCFLQmVuLPHXsoYc.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:39:35', '2024-01-16 09:39:35', 1, 'zannier-hotels-bai-san-ho', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Zannier Hotels Bai San Hô offers 5-star accommodations in Song Cau and features free bikes, outdoor swimming pool and garden. Featuring family rooms, this property also provides guests with a playground. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3878.7367854337663!2d109.27336697497869!3d13.55173178681952!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f75d6b23541e7%3A0