(74, 'Stelia Beach Resort', 'Lô C1, Độc Lập, Phường 9, Tuy Hòa, Phú Yên 62000, Vietnam', 0, '02573666678', NULL, 'http://steliabeachresort.com/', '<p>Stelia Beach Resort features a restaurant, outdoor swimming pool, a bar and shared lounge in Tuy Hoa. With free WiFi, this 5-star resort has a garden and a private beach area. The accommodations offers a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests. The units come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a coffee machine, a shower, a hairdryer and a desk. All rooms are fitted with a shared bathroom with a bath and free toiletries. At the resort every room includes a wardrobe and a private bathroom. A buffet breakfast is available every morning at Stelia Beach Resort. The accommodations offers a sun terrace. The area is popular for cycling, and bike hire and car hire are available at Stelia Beach Resort. The nearest airport is Tuy Hoa Airport, 6.5 mi from the resort.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/tHaaZDTQYXJZK464zoDE.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/OgSBUEorfsUpYstaWRet.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:41:09', '2024-01-16 09:41:09', 1, 'stelia-beach-resort', NULL, 'Stelia Beach Resort features a restaurant, outdoor swimming pool, a bar and shared lounge in Tuy Hoa. With free WiFi, this 5-star resort has a garden and a private beach area. The accommodations offers a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3885.7725534218175!2d109.30494117497076!3d13.113590287214969!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316fedf5286b5b99%3A0xb61fec4369cc3130!2sStelia%20Beach%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398046417!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"p