(76, 'Mandala Hotel & Spa Phú Yên', 'ĐL Hùng Vương, Phường 7, Tuy Hòa, Phú Yên 56000, Vietnam', 0, '02573868866', NULL, 'https://mandalahotels.com.vn/mandala-phu-yen/', '<p>Located in Tuy Hoa, a 18-minute walk from Tuy Hoa Beach, Mandala Hotel &amp; Spa Ph&uacute; Y&ecirc;n has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. With a terrace, the property also has a restaurant, as well as a bar. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a closet, an electric tea pot, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a private bathroom with a shower. Mandala Hotel &amp; Spa Ph&uacute; Y&ecirc;n has a playground. There\'s an in-house snack bar and guests can also use the business area. The nearest airport is Tuy Hoa Airport, 3.7 miles from the accommodation.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/TczVcaK27nGtV17MHYmp.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/p6VTActtTlmpzqiJao7T.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:43:46', '2024-01-16 09:43:46', 1, 'mandala-hotel-and-spa-phu-yen', NULL, 'Located in Tuy Hoa, a 18-minute walk from Tuy Hoa Beach, Mandala Hotel & Spa Phú Yên has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a shared lounge. With a terrace, the property also has a restaurant, as well as a bar. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3885.935090402573!2d109.30247657881274!3d13.103298554283036!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316fed3ea3aa4225%3A0xf45372d2822adcdc!2sMandala%20Hotel%20%26%20Spa%20Ph%C3%BA%20Y%C3%AAn!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398202822!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaur