(79, 'Dankbaar Resort Quy Nhon', '01 Hàn Mặc Tử, Ghềnh Ráng, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định, Vietnam', 0, '0967386666', NULL, 'https://dankbaarresort.com/', '<p>With leisure facilities including an outdoor pool and spa, Dankbaar Resort Quy Nhon offers 4-star comfort in the city center. Overlooking Quy Nhon&rsquo;s coast, it has free Wi-Fi and parking. Featuring classic wood furnishings and spacious layouts, elegant air-conditioned rooms have private balconies with views of the garden or sea. For convenience, guests have the use of a safe, fridge and free tea/coffee making amenities. Enjoy soothing massages at Royal Healthcare&rsquo;s spa or maintain regular workouts at the fitness center. Day trips to attractions like Ham Ho Ecological Park and Nui Mot Lake can be planned at the tour desk. A range of Chinese dishes and local specialties can be sampled at Asian Restaurant. Ship Restaurant offers the experience of being on board with its unique architecture and Western fare. Dankbaar Resort Quy Nhon is easily accessible from Han Mac Tu Hill and Queen&rsquo;s Beach. It is 19 mi from Phu Cat Airport.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/vuPEai92j0lPBF8AJJsJ.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/9cYVeU9zN0qqnqgRwUW2.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:47:58', '2024-01-16 09:47:58', 1, 'dankbaar-resort-quy-nhon', NULL, 'With leisure facilities including an outdoor pool and spa, Dankbaar Resort Quy Nhon offers 4-star comfort in the city center. Overlooking Quy Nhon’s coast, it has free Wi-Fi and parking.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.536446150736!2d109.20914727889225!3d13.746491652209354!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6d87011f78f7%3A0xd32eaa02292f3d27!2sDANKBAAR%20RESORT!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398459688!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 10),
