(81, 'L\'amor Boutique Hotel Quy Nhơn', '1H1 Nguyễn Thị Định, Nguyễn Văn Cừ, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định 55000, Vietnam', 0, '02562226868', NULL, 'https://lamorboutiquehotel.com/', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon, a 10-minute walk from Quy Nhon Beach, L\'amor Boutique Hotel Quy Nhơn has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. This 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. The hotel has a terrace and city views, and guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant or a drink at the bar. All rooms include air conditioning and a flat-screen TV, and some rooms at the hotel have a sea view. All rooms will provide guests with a minibar. Breakfast is available every morning, and includes buffet, &agrave; la carte and American options. Guests can use the business center or relax in the snack bar. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 21 miles from L\'amor Boutique Hotel Quy Nhơn.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/yYIwyWzo6FmcbGmanGpx.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/vC5luDGqWLrpbzC6dtSF.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:49:48', '2024-01-16 09:49:48', 1, 'l-amor-boutique-hotel-quy-nhon', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon, a 10-minute walk from Quy Nhon Beach, L\'amor Boutique Hotel Quy Nhơn has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. This 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. The hotel has a terrace and city views, and guests can enjoy a meal at the restaurant or a drink at the bar.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.3923804285037!2d109.2101227749825!3d13.755195286637013!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6db8eab4ae27%3A0x79687262c79c9ab4!2zTCdBbW9yIEJvdXRpcXVlIEhvdGVsIFF1eSBOaMahbiAtIEtow6FjaCBz4bqhbiBn4bqnbiBiaeG7g24gdmlldyAzNjAgdG_DoG4gdGjDoG5oIHBo4buR!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398562327!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 10),
(82, 'Grand Hyams Hotel - Quy Nhon Beach', '28 Nguyễn Huệ, Phường Lê Lợi, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định 55000, Vietnam', 0, '02563906666', NULL, 'https://www.grandhyamshotel.com/', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon and with Quy Nhon Beach reachable within a 2-minute walk, Grand Hyams Hotel - Quy Nhon Beach has concierge services, allergy-free rooms, a garden, free WiFi and a shared lounge. Offering a restaurant, the property also has free bikes, as well as an indoor pool and a fitness center. The property provides a kids\' club, room service and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a terrace and a private bathroom with a shower. At Grand Hyams Hotel - Quy Nhon Beach rooms come with bed linen and towels. The daily breakfast offers buffet, continental or American options. The accommodation has a playground. Guests will find a 24-hour front desk, a business center and ironing service at the property. Bai Rang Beach is 1.4 miles from Grand Hyams Hotel - Quy Nhon Beach. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 21 miles from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/4UvPPnuvGKLziYDZk3nA.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/PkIj56dTsUeGynhYYA73.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:51:11', '2024-01-16 09:51:11', 1, 'grand-hyams-hotel-quy-nhon-beach', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon and with Quy Nhon Beach reachable within a 2-minute walk, Grand Hyams Hotel - Quy Nhon Beach has concierge services, allergy-free rooms, a garden, free WiFi and a shared lounge. Offering a restaurant, the property also has free bikes, as well as an indoor pool and a fitness center. The property provides a kids\' club, room service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.143609958861!2d109.23065127498279!3d13.770211886623597!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6c89ae885305%3A0xe2b7f5f96d62ffaf!2sGrand%20Hyams%20Hotel%20-%20Quy%20Nhon%20Beach!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398652494!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 10),
(83, 'Danang Marriott Resort & Spa', 'No. 7 Truong Sa Street, Hoa Hai Ward, Ngu Hanh Son District, Danang, Vietnam –', 5, '02363968888', NULL, 'http://www.marriott.com/hotels/travel/dadmr-danang-marriott-resort--spa/?scid=f2ae0541-1279-4f24-b197-a979c79310b0', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Get the celebrity treatment with world-class service at Danang Marriott Resort &amp; Spa</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">With the Marble Mountains as a backdrop, Danang Marriott Resort &amp; Spa offers luxurious accommodations by the unspoiled sands of Non Nuoc Beach. It houses 5 outdoor pools, a full-service spa and fitness facilities. Featuring modern interiors, spacious rooms have private balconies with stunning sea or pool views and outdoor seating. They come with a 46-inch flat-screen cable TV, ample lounge area and yoga mats. Leisurely afternoons can be spent by the private beachfront or snorkeling in clear waters. Added conveniences include free internet access, a business center and tour desk. Hearty breakfast buffets and all-day dining are available at Goji Kitchen + Bar while Madame Son Restaurant serves Vietnamese dishes. Light refreshments can be found at Great Room, Writer\'s Bar and Non Nuoc Bar. Danang Marriott Resort &amp; Spa is 15 minutes&rsquo; drive from Da Nang International Airport. It is 19 mi from the UNESCO Heritage Site of Hoi An.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.8</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/ByZ3OUXedInoSOBZfwRO.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/bS49wZCb2YyX3knboeKZ.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:52:08', '2024-01-16 09:52:08', 1, 'danang-marriott-resort-and-spa', NULL, 'With the Marble Mountains as a backdrop, Danang Marriott Resort & Spa offers luxurious accommodations by the unspoiled sands of Non Nuoc Beach. It houses 5 outdoor pools, a full-service spa and fitness facilities.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3835.126919789796!2d108.26337367414972!3d16.006907184663557!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314210cbebc12213%3A0xc6fc741592df54ec!2sDanang%20Marriott%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705398697572!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(84, 'Fleur de Lys Hotel Quy Nhon', '16 Nguyễn Huệ, Phường Lê Lợi, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định, Vietnam', 0, '02563666888', NULL, 'https://fleurdelys.vn/', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon, a 2-minute walk from Quy Nhon Beach, Fleur de Lys Hotel Quy Nhon has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers room service, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi. The property provides a concierge service, a tour desk and currency exchange for guests. Some rooms contain a kitchenette with a fridge, a microwave and a minibar. Breakfast is available each morning, and includes buffet, continental and American options. At the hotel you\'ll find a restaurant serving Cantonese, Chinese and Seafood cuisine. Vegetarian, dairy-free and vegan options can also be requested. Bai Rang Beach is a 19-minute walk from Fleur de Lys Hotel Quy Nhon. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 21 miles from the accommodation.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/CvoGvE4ATnGBEEtmmFfL.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/LSVKqT2DK6CC1S99NC2K.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:52:42', '2024-01-16 09:52:42', 1, 'fleur-de-lys-hotel-quy-nhon', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon, a 2-minute walk from Quy Nhon Beach, Fleur de Lys Hotel Quy Nhon has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers room service, a 24-hour front desk and free WiFi. The property provides a concierge service, a tour desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.1279607602273!2d109.23370537498272!3d13.771155986622754!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6d9380fb77bd%3A0x836fd2d60569dce4!2sFleur%20De%20Lys%20Hotel%20Quy%20Nhon!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398736833!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"24