(85, 'Awaken Da Nang Hotel', '148 Võ Nguyên Giáp, P. Phước Mỹ, Q. Sơn Trà, Da Nang, Vietnam', 5, '02363985888', NULL, 'http://awakenhotel.com/', '<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Get the celebrity treatment with world-class service at Awaken Da Nang Hotel</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Situated in Da Nang, 700 metres from My Khe Beach, Awaken Da Nang Hotel features accommodation with a fitness centre, free private parking, a terrace and a restaurant. With free WiFi, this 5-star hotel offers a kids\' club and room service. The hotel provides an indoor pool and a 24-hour front desk. The rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Rooms are equipped with a kettle, while some rooms include a balcony and others also boast sea views. All rooms will provide guests with a fridge. A buffet, continental or American breakfast is available each morning at the property. Guests can make use of the business centre or relax in the bar. Song Han Bridge is 2.6 km from Awaken Da Nang Hotel, while Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 3.2 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 6 km from the accommodation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'hotels/January2024/tGaZvvcN1k13icerq4VY.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/syObxnBpPxMEkE0kvGv3.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:55:24', '2024-01-16 09:55:24', 1, 'awaken-da-nang-hotel', NULL, 'Situated in Da Nang, 700 metres from My Khe Beach, Awaken Da Nang Hotel features accommodation with a fitness centre, free private parking, a terrace and a restaurant. With free WiFi, this 5-star hotel offers a kids\' club and room service. The hotel provides an indoor pool and a 24-hour front desk.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.8009204596024!2d108.24198867415154!3d16.075817284604618!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314217b9f5689797%3A0xeb0b6cfbc1bd35ea!2sAwaken%20Danang%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705398870265!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(86, 'Anya Premier Hotel Quy Nhon', '44 An Dương Vương, Nguyễn Văn Cừ, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định 59000, Vietnam', 0, '02562222268', NULL, 'http://anyapremierhotelquynhon.com/', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon, a few steps from Quy Nhon Beach, Anya Premier Hotel Quy Nhon provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. The property features a bar, as well as a restaurant serving American cuisine. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a shared lounge and free WiFi. All rooms at the hotel are equipped with a seating area. Complete with a private bathroom equipped with a shower and free toiletries, guest rooms at Anya Premier Hotel Quy Nhon have a flat-screen TV and air conditioning, and selected rooms come with a terrace. All guest rooms include a safety deposit box. Breakfast is available daily, and includes buffet, continental and vegetarian options. Guests can use the business center or relax in the snack bar. Queen\'s Beach is a 17-minute walk from the accommodation. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 20 miles from Anya Premier Hotel Quy Nhon.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/Q1N3wlm00GPwvx5Ej9Lg.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/ws9kQeM39UdMZoW7a0Js.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:55:33', '2024-01-16 09:55:33', 1, 'anya-premier-hotel-quy-nhon', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon, a few steps from Quy Nhon Beach, Anya Premier Hotel Quy Nhon provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. The property features a bar, as well as a restaurant serving American cuisine. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a shared lounge and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3875.4366029582884!2d109.21286147498243!3d13.752524186639432!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6dcb86f7ae17%3A0x598c09d1e98a3a84!2sANYA%20PREMIER%20HOTEL%20QUY%20NHON!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705398914905!5m