(87, 'Anantara Quy Nhon Villas', 'Cầu Bãi Dại, Ghềnh Ráng, Thành phố Qui Nhơn, Bình Định, Vietnam', 0, '02563840077', NULL, 'https://www.anantara.com/quy-nhon?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=ANQuyNhon&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon, a 9-minute walk from Bai Xep Beach, Anantara Quy Nhon Villas has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared lounge, along with free WiFi. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. Rooms include a private bathroom, while certain rooms contain a terrace and others also feature a sea view. A continental breakfast is available each morning at the hotel. Guests can use the business center or relax in the bar. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 26 miles from Anantara Quy Nhon Villas.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/pguEfMn6Yiwlm1cA8LuZ.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/8MRp3RPT2f7iyUGCcLzs.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:57:14', '2024-01-16 09:57:14', 1, 'anantara-quy-nhon-villas', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon, a 9-minute walk from Bai Xep Beach, Anantara Quy Nhon Villas has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared lounge, along with free WiFi. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3876.625786797956!2d109.23023267498098!3d13.680504086703973!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f6db19d7bd4c5%3A0x973445a204dc362c!2sAnantara%20Quy%20Nhon%20Villas!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705399014740!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '