(88, 'Furama Resort Danang', '105 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, Khue My Ward, Ngu Hanh Son District, Da Nang, Vietnam', 5, '02363847333', NULL, 'https://furamavietnam.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience world-class service at Furama Resort Danang</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">A luxurious stay at Furama Resort Danang begins your journey to UNESCO-listed sites like Hue Imperial City, located a 2-hour drive from the resort. World-class facilities like freshwater pools, a spa, and 4 dining options await guests. Furama Resort Danang is nestled on Bac My An. It is a 30-minute drive from the ancient \"Silk Road\" trading port of Hoi An and is less than 2 hours from My Son Holy Land. Tastefully designed, the spacious air-conditioned rooms all feature a private balcony offering tropical views. They are fitted with timber flooring and elegant carpets, and come with walk-in closet, ample seating space and large marble bathrooms. The Furama offers deluxe beauty and spa treatments that include a variety of massage styles and facials. Guests can relax with steam baths and sauna sessions, or enjoy a massage by the pool. The on-site Water Sport House provides equipment for windsurfing, ocean kayaking and water skiing. The resort also offers yoga and Tai Chi classes on the beach. Younger guests will enjoy the cinema and games room which is equipped with Play Station 3. Caf&eacute; Indochine serves a wide range of international and pan-Asian cuisines in a French colonial setting. There is also Don Cipriani&rsquo;s which serves traditional Italian cuisines. Hai Van Lounge is one of the three bars with nightly performance by Filipino bands.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.8</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/N25YwvTJdrzRWExbRlVk.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/S4Qo6cWLBrbFaJ3yINyb.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 09:57:46', '2024-01-16 09:57:46', 1, 'furama-resort-danang', NULL, 'A luxurious stay at Furama Resort Danang begins your journey to UNESCO-listed sites like Hue Imperial City, located a 2-hour drive from the resort. World-class facilities like freshwater pools, a spa, and 4 dining options await guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d7668.945778792182!2d108.24296035276649!3d16.040932140991004!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31420fdbc8cc38ef%3A0x9a6a3e31121225d2!2sFurama%20Resort%20Danang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705399025303!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16);
