(89, 'Avani Quy Nhon Resort', 'Ghenh Rang,, Bai Dai Beach, Bình Định, Vietnam', 0, '02563840132', NULL, 'https://www.avanihotels.com/quy-nhon?utm_source=GoogleMyBusiness&utm_medium=GMB&utm_term=QuyNhon&utm_content=Home&utm_campaign=Google_GMB', '<p>Located along the private Bai Dai Beach, award-winning Avani Quy Nhon Resort features rooms with Medieval Vietnamese d&eacute;cor and balconies with sea views. An outdoor cliff-top restaurant is offered. Avani Quy Nhon Resort\'s rooms feature open spaces and calming colors. Rooms are generously equipped with flat-screen TVs, mini-bar and tea/coffee makers. Marble/tiled floors and a sea-facing seating area provide guests with a tranquil experience. Guests can enjoy kayaking and watersports on the private beach, or take a refreshing swim in the pool. The spa offers wellness and massage services. TRE Restaurant, located atop a cliff, serves the best of Eastern and Western cuisine and seafood, while GIO Bar and Lounge offers coffee, snacks and tropical cocktails. Avani Quy Nhon Resort is located in the charming seaside town of Binh Dinh, 6.2 mi from Quy Nhon City Center. Quy Nhon Airport is 22 mi away.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/b1L4YEd1QxVDdSrFgH54.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/oMh9y08rxDcduwEShw3t.png\"]', '2024-01-16 09:59:59', '2024-01-16 09:59:59', 1, 'avani-quy-nhon-resort', NULL, 'Located along the private Bai Dai Beach, award-winning Avani Quy Nhon Resort features rooms with Medieval Vietnamese décor and balconies with sea views. An outdoor cliff-top restaurant is offered.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3876.605184410204!2d109.23001807498107!3d13.681754986702808!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f7289aa9f0751%3A0x55e1b44380dc205e!2sAvani%20Quy%20Nhon%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705399161843!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\