(90, 'Naman Retreat', 'Truong Sa street, Hoa Hai ward, Ngu Hanh Son district, Da Nang, Vietnam', 5, '02363959888', NULL, 'https://namanretreat.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience world-class service at Naman Retreat</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at Naman Retreat! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?lang=en-gb&amp;dt=1705399102&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;state=Uv0DXk7utcQPMgAK4NMLaEUO1ElwU1d7FYbE2uVCMYouYdOIsQ_UKMtvdaYDtmy6ZQ_J1KcqvgYPDvyoAF7ENzrJmhIxo0FkETi7q5PwikZmBi6s3TqEpHsOMolTvOnmaZDhA6AsTRxECQVU9IntBlETuu2j0CXrkwBFLj-MkRDHH7YqRQtL-8nsAX9fX29miq2P0qiL8_oEsLPbMR1ntkmumGvZeCvNujME11pxC6HUiYo_3-W8OJ07UgMuDe58CQWZJle3pUdu8F3m9UhOlc9zyZF1XRZF7We2zyX6XpwrQytwXOdIxeJs-UCyeGaF0IXennEcxWg69D1dODlmYqqQuiiKsplXMZ4AdQDq9kQejRe1LrJdEqIUPAdUQbsRVvh4AzuGchBU0ZqppjYmYaBVb68tzSoGlc9ynAG-kaB1QlJG6sxnLjt6UP8WnxH_AKFVNlXecHuyvyTD1T0aKWMxiomfSBdhR_T8k6HDHTp6YejUtytlNIWpPvyL4tqkEpTeD-j4-d1Y0w3oh2-t1hrWnTxB_csAiL2ahGd7_oJCRJjv9B85KNk6tBfkwmP6-9z7mIYeYWIct3Td5DtntXrb28ihMoITqd3-fDUlp5tTURw-OuvfkPdsgHBxiRuj-oC_PDtfSr4vzM0H3S5vTjWakYlSOh_aZrtGyZkHk3E&amp;response_type=sso&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;aid=357028&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located opposite the two popular golf courses of Montgomerie Links Vietnam, Naman Retreat welcomes guests with an outdoor swimming pool and a private beach area. Rooms are luxuriously furnished and fitted with free WiFi access. The peaceful getaway is situated in Da Nang only 4.2 km from Non Nuoc Hamlet and Non Nuoc Beach. The majestic Ngu Hanh Son Mountain is about 5 km away while Phu Bai Airport is located 79 km away. Naman Retreat offers spacious rooms and villas. Each is fitted with air conditioning and a flat-screen TV. Some villas feature a separate living area and a private pool. Elegant en suite bathrooms feature a bathtub and plush bathrobes. Private yoga and Reiki (healing therapy) are also available. Other amenities include a fitness centre, barbeque facilities and an outdoor terrace. Guests can also enjoy several activities at Naman Retreat like cooking class, lantern making and kite making. An array of local and international cuisines will be served Naman Retreat Restaurant. In-room dining options are possible. Friendly English-speaking staff at the 24-hour front desk can arrange for airport transfers and shuttle services. The property offers a welcome drink upon arrival and complimentary daily bus tours to Danang City and Hoi An Ancient Town.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.2</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/8HWTVehmKhIwwFh0Qd9j.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/e6YzQBtvwy1Vl4LDueTZ.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 10:00:36', '2024-01-16 10:00:36', 1, 'naman-retreat', NULL, 'Located opposite the two popular golf courses of Montgomerie Links Vietnam, Naman Retreat welcomes guests with an outdoor swimming pool and a private beach area. Rooms are luxuriously furnished and fitted with free WiFi access.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d5424.700344551844!2d108.28237739619004!3d15.969604562948419!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314210ffff49be83%3A0x4dc264a06ef8baa5!2sNaman%20Retreat!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705399188239!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(91, 'Maia Resort Quy Nhon', 'W6HW+RC, Nhon Hoi Economic Zone, Cat Tien Ward, Phù Cát, Bình Định 820000, Vietnam', 0, '02562206688', NULL, 'http://maiaresortquynhon.com/', '<p>Located in Quy Nhon, a few steps from Trung Luong Beach, Maia Resort Quy Nhon provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a garden and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property has a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests. All guest rooms at the resort are equipped with a seating area, a flat-screen TV and a safety deposit box. Featuring a private bathroom with a shower and a hairdryer, certain units at Maia Resort Quy Nhon also provide guests with a pool view. The rooms include a closet. The nearest airport is Phu Cat Airport, 13 miles from the accommodation.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/70akti1xmd37GyWLLbxu.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/lqGF3qlXsNGS6EB17Rzu.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:01:14', '2024-01-16 10:01:14', 1, 'maia-resort-quy-nhon', NULL, 'Located in Quy Nhon, a few steps from Trung Luong Beach, Maia Resort Quy Nhon provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a garden and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property has a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3872.4764154163713!2d109.24174307498578!3d13.930214986480506!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x316f411ae6d6f15d%3A0xf1f4dde8747e523!2sMaia%20Resort%20Quy%20Nhon!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705399253171!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\