(92, 'Celina Peninsula Resort Quảng Bình', 'Võ Nguyên Giáp, Street, Đồng Hới, Quảng Bình 510000, Vietnam', 0, '02323900999', NULL, 'http://celinaresort.com/', '<p>Located in Dương Cảnh, a 10-minute walk from Nhat Le Beach, Celina Peninsula Resort Quảng B&igrave;nh provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi. The resort has a terrace and a 24-hour front desk. The resort will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony and a private bathroom with a bidet. At Celina Peninsula Resort Quảng B&igrave;nh all rooms come with bed linen and towels. A buffet, &agrave; la carte or Asian breakfast is available every morning at the property. The accommodation has a playground. The nearest airport is Dong Hoi Airport, 6.2 miles from Celina Peninsula Resort Quảng B&igrave;nh.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/oXft4I3pimR4HTPO9qHG.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/cwKYUMyxcZymmYtkXKiT.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:02:58', '2024-01-16 10:02:58', 1, 'celina-peninsula-resort-quang-binh', NULL, 'Located in Dương Cảnh, a 10-minute walk from Nhat Le Beach, Celina Peninsula Resort Quảng Bình provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi. The resort has a terrace and a 24-hour front desk.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3805.9849642614245!2d106.63978877942269!3d17.460433740738445!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314751abfd75af21%3A0x60f2ced29f3b0218!2sCelina%20Peninsula%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705399359230!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"laz