(94, 'Melia Danang Beach Resort', '19 Truong Sa, Hoa Hai Ward, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang, Vietnam', 5, '02363929888', NULL, 'https://www.melia.com/en/hotels/vietnam/danang/melia-danang-beach-resort?utm_medium=organic&utm_source=directories&utm_campaign=google&utm_content=5752', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience world-class service at Melia Danang Beach Resort</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at Melia Danang Beach Resort! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;dt=1705399297&amp;response_type=sso&amp;lang=en-gb&amp;state=UvoDXk7utcQPMgBFbunuxXZNI0KUWXs_DccqAZj6A9NW5fs5H7aS-afgq3xYsg-8gq_MBtVBErQKELgLGj1idXWgt1Tje-5mtcWkP5PltJrzx7O9izMowPjkrc5RgN8cy2Ae-ZdzvuEBhrlxTbjNOQOlnz2d1mMe7rQhPqB9OBNgBbiTbVd-bYviFoHN8wnSbW_QIyjWZVjvlr-nBwg8HDzD16ge11fHK6lg1SvzsVe88Svpjc5YSF0OCdjAdi_sd1KkZbDzO6AJsQn_Mw2g90OBVbCxVL_0UzT5zRFy7YJWxC6z02Bh5IdSn7D2tjhWPFN_kB0E92DcW4IYOtiIfX1s6LAwM664_tUOVZuNv57YenHkYG6wlMQVr2i16c8V_eiCNf6t2qxJAF81weshUN2ARnBLAhHCuY4B2LIsTfQJ7IKHexJOhPeCWqs7wrepjzSdMeou0vh2m7grGLwlmAy86h5rI3mCtl3NCVtfPsovFMdg1LHhK2GsEoOP_g_kueOfh7hBfA1ZmSWaKNsrzZAGeTtYAGS48lPfcsNjJ5ePLPUQ17j--2HRnRRUydwvgtvNmIlwlBz6eqhECIvNRXukwHhyK5SLFlDSmHxwZF33_xPwhnNa3jN0nyrdXCq11jr28RCVqFStIYwL8RjDCFGQ8XmJbrQYB1nC8bI&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;aid=357028\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Si