e parking is available on site and complimentary WiFi access is provided throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d1917.6257720547464!2d108.26701803766832!3d16.00041579826435!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314210c5cab81527%3A0xfd5b35311bbbd0fc!2sMeli%C3%A1%20Danang%20Beach%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705399445219!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(95, 'Seabird Hotel Thien Cam', 'Bãi biển, Cẩm Nhượng, Hà Tĩnh, 45000, Vietnam', 0, '0982783909', NULL, 'http://seabirdhotel.vn/', '<p>Facing the beachfront, Seabird Hotel Thien Cam offers 4-star accommodations in H&agrave; Tĩnh and features an outdoor swimming pool, garden and terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests. All guest rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Every room includes an electric tea pot, while some rooms come with a balcony and others also have sea views. At Seabird Hotel Thien Cam all rooms are equipped with bed linen and towels. The nearest airport is Vinh International Airport, 50 miles from the accommodation.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/2wqeh6KSRx5My5XJrkCO.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/uki0KKKHWpRG2CEGUIey.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:06:20', '2024-01-16 10:06:20', 1, 'seabird-hotel-thien-cam', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Seabird Hotel Thien Cam offers 4-star accommodations in Hà Tĩnh and features an outdoor swimming pool, garden and terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3788.5454616306706!2d106.09415577508027!3d18.276647082770193!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31385d7ac01cf439%3A0x40a28bb632e90729!2zU2VhYmlyZCBIb3RlbCBUaGnDqm4gQ-G6p20!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705399560168!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade