(96, 'TIA Wellness Resort', '109 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, Khue My Ward, Ngu Hanh Son District, Da Nang, Vietnam', 5, '02363967999', NULL, 'https://tiawellnessresort.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience world-class service at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inclusive! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?bkng_action=hotel&amp;aid=357028&amp;response_type=sso&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;state=UogEXk7utcQPMgBcphjeLa9PpDjshqlnw7X5_fyZ3dsBkuXgPw8YV_Zgjk9VkFomcCr442ASE0sgKd4XCYX5emJUvHjErDJfkQdwGyatctaShIgGN1eKBZN3i2uJB1oPIx_zkxbB-khVMj7nvhmmnL24LgGI-3e09fxLyQs4-maW2wHtZYziFnkCOJj8XPfEjx_-dfGNG8tBqndr1WGK03EGARKhheDYaYlSwos9rXy-YfH9nQzGaQd8wnm-_NF_y7KJPQd9aGcO9w5la-gpWJJlrVu9eaagO71wQ7LyopU1ey5Nt63WsrkYiT1cDI-zhZY7HQgYLiCPseSjpRFZ7Usu_Fv0jsp3hpkvHd0eAcgxHvkvPFOTsdgUuOezv8ciUHJTD_g8EogjDOYKWx7cBbkDBhr125oQwqt1SdF0XZCo4_Uj-DhuYPtBPho7NabCgtmJTkxZaKe8bgszA584lZ96L7hIn7mR1rfwwyXe2hbfx_akRgi5WXNEW13_yNR7Zw1lSn-4QADvlc2xXnY8yKtDVkXAYfLiFUYmfJb_6lGlafdhQ3hDPSKGyYrBy-qp9a6XOk_pIISksTajD_nJgD_TspJLIz54pqEKeaPUf72sG3Mh9eD7u4aikwbmvDF_rZp4cmMKW4bHZ-6vRpB0REP20d0PM4k8TfuM9jtG1aotkjnUj3h9QVZ-Fg&amp;lang=en-gb&amp;dt=1705399538&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located on the beautiful My Khe Beach, TIA Wellness Resort - Spa Inc