(97, 'Silk Path Grand Hue Hotel', '2 Lê Lợi, Vĩnh Ninh, Thành phố Huế, Thừa Thiên Huế, Vietnam', 5, '02343975555', NULL, 'https://silkpathhotel.com/', '<p>Located in Hue, 1.2 miles from Trang Tien Bridge, Silk Path Grand Hue Hotel has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared lounge, along with free WiFi. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms offering a desk, an electric tea pot, a minibar, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a bidet. All rooms feature a closet. Guests at Silk Path Grand Hue Hotel can enjoy a buffet or a continental breakfast. The accommodation has a terrace. There\'s an in-house bar and guests can also use the business area. Popular points of interest near Silk Path Grand Hue Hotel include Hue Railway Station, Ho Chi Minh Museum and Bao Quoc Pagoda. The nearest airport is Phu Bai International, 8.7 miles from the hotel, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/sRWv8MOU5cFdiXIvjXBN.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/gbcAqlU2ur8Hps06CqqS.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:08:05', '2024-01-16 10:08:05', 1, 'silk-path-grand-hue-hotel', NULL, 'Located in Hue, 1.2 miles from Trang Tien Bridge, Silk Path Grand Hue Hotel has accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and a shared lounge, along with free WiFi. The property provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3826.351030372099!2d107.57715857503771!3d16.457753784279493!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3141a131f0123adf%3A0x6429daefb2790a9!2sSilk%20Path%2