(104, 'Wink Hotel Danang Centr', '178 Đường Trần Phú, Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363831999', NULL, '178 Đường Trần Phú, Danang, Vietnam', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in Danang, a 7-minute walk from Cham Museum, Wink Hotel Danang Centre - Full 24hrs stay upon check-in has accommodations with a fitness center, free private parking, a restaurant and a bar. This 4-star hotel offers a 24-hour front desk and a business center. The property is a 7-minute walk from Indochina Riverside Mall, and within 1.3 miles of the city center. At the hotel rooms have air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Wink Hotel Danang Centre - Full 24hrs stay upon check-in provides certain accommodations with city views, and rooms contain an electric tea pot. The rooms will provide guests with a fridge. A buffet, &agrave; la carte or continental breakfast is available each morning at the property. Song Han Bridge is a 12-minute walk from the accommodation, while Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 0.9 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 1.9 miles from Wink Hotel Danang Centre - Full 24hrs stay upon check-in.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.7</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/21UawLf1iTTY5dEtFSlx.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/RFOMKnCxtAXyoLfHDlTW.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 10:23:01', '2024-01-16 10:23:01', 1, 'wink-hotel-danang-centr', NULL, 'Located in Danang, a 7-minute walk from Cham Museum, Wink Hotel Danang Ce