(106, 'Stella Maris Beach Danang', '3 Vo Van Kiet, Phuoc My Ward, Son Tra District, Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363555657', NULL, 'https://stellamarisbeachdanang.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Stella Maris Beach Danang has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, a shared lounge and terrace in Danang. The property features a bar, as well as a restaurant serving Vietnamese cuisine. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi throughout the property. The rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Stella Maris Beach Danang provides some accommodations with city views, and rooms are equipped with an electric tea pot. All guest rooms will provide guests with a fridge. A buffet, continental or American breakfast is available each morning at the property. Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around Danang, like cycling. My Khe Beach is a 15-minute walk from Stella Maris Beach Danang, while Bac My An Beach is 1.4 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 3.1 miles from the hotel.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.7</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/KjSxG3Ek6JAysBbXlkFA.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/aOaRns8vyYZn8rlJc0qz.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 10:26:14', '2024-01-16 10:26:14', 1, 'stella-maris-beach-danang', NULL, 'Stella Maris Beach Danang has an outdoor swimming pool, fitness center, a sha