(107, 'The Arena Cam Ranh', 'Cam Nghĩa, Cam Ranh, Khánh Hòa, Vietnam', 0, '02583968888', NULL, 'http://thearena.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">A good location for a stress-free stay in Miếu &Ocirc;ng, The Arena Cam Ranh Kh&aacute;nh Ho&agrave;- Việt Nam is an apartment surrounded by views of the lake. The property features a private beach area, infinity pool, and parking on-site among other facilities. A fitness room is available for guests. The apartment provides sea views, a sun terrace, a 24-hour front desk, and free Wifi is available throughout the property. The apartment complex will provide guests with air-conditioned units offering a desk, a kettle, a fridge, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV, a balcony, and a private bathroom with a walk-in shower. A patio with an outdoor dining area and pool views is offered in every unit. At the apartment complex, every unit has bed linen and towels. A mini-market is available at the apartment. Kids pool is also available at the apartment, while guests can also relax in the garden. 100 Egg Mud Bath is 17 miles from The Arena Cam Ranh Kh&aacute;nh Ho&agrave;- Việt Nam, while Alexandre Yersin Museum is 21 miles away. The nearest airport is Cam Ranh International Airport, 2.5 miles from the accommodation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>', 'hotels/January2024/dTRAaCdYb71DqXMpaE22.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/x4LWr9Fj25Wj61Re6kbE.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:28:37', '2024-01-16 10:28:37', 1, 'the-arena-cam-ranh', NULL, 'A good location for a stress-free stay in Miếu Ông, The Arena Cam Ranh Khánh Hoà- Việt Nam is an apartment surrounded by views of the lake. The property features a private beach area, infinity pool, and parking on-site among other facilities. A fitness room is available for guests. The apartment provides sea views, a sun terrace, a 24-hour front desk, and free Wifi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3902.2544929732985!2d109.21191587473126!3d12.025992688209216!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3170f4f27d8e84b5%3A0xa16cb25d2b46bf10!2sThe%20Arena%20Cam%20Ranh!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705400894422!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 14),
(108, 'Hilton Garden Inn Da Nang', '96 Vo Nguyen Giap Street, 550000 Danang, Vietnam', 5, '02363780000', NULL, 'https://www.hilton.com/en/hotels/daddagi-hilton-garden-inn-da-nang/?SEO_id=GMB-APAC-GI-DADDAGI', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in Danang, a few steps from My Khe Beach, Hilton Garden Inn Da Nang provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers a bar. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi. The hotel will provide guests with air-conditioned rooms with a desk, an electric tea pot, a fridge, a safety deposit box, a flat-screen TV and a private bathroom with a bidet. Guest rooms include a closet. The daily breakfast offers buffet, &agrave; la carte or continental options. At Hilton Garden Inn Da Nang you\'ll find a restaurant serving Vietnamese, Local and Asian cuisine. Vegetarian, vegan and gluten-free options can also be requested. Song Han Bridge is 2 miles from the accommodation, while Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 2.4 miles away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 4.3 miles from Hilton Garden Inn Da Nang.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.0</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/ZOHHInkyvbgFoXvoIoI2.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/tCvw9o3wUBXJSTd2Gfn9.jpg\"]', '2024-01-16 10:30:05', '2024-01-16 10:30:05', 1, 'hilton-garden-inn-da-nang', NULL, 'Located in Danang, a few steps from My Khe Beach, Hilton Garden Inn Da Nang provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a terrace. This 4-star hotel offers a bar. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.718661765085!2d108.2438983741516!3d16.080082667102985!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142178c34d665a1%3A0x9e09484a48315c8c!2sHilton%20Garden%20Inn%20Da%20Nang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705400963359!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(109, 'Hôtel Colline', '10 Phan Bội Châu, Phường 1, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 670000, Vietnam', 5, '02633665588', NULL, 'http://hotelcolline.com/', '<p>Located in the heart of Dalat city, 1640 feet from Lam Vien Square, H&ocirc;tel Colline provides a bar and rooms with free WiFi access. This hotel is located 656 feet from Xuan Huong Lake. The hotel has a restaurant, and Yersin Park Da Lat is 1640 feet away. The units come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a kettle, a bidet, free toiletries and a desk. Featuring a private bathroom, rooms at the hotel also boast a city view. All units feature a wardrobe. Guests at H&ocirc;tel Colline can enjoy a buffet breakfast. Speaking English and Vietnamese at the 24-hour front desk, staff are willing to help at any time of the day. Dalat Flower Gardens is 1640 feet from the accommodations, while Truc Lam Temple is 2.5 mi away. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 14 mi from the property.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/jHXulAv90r2IxSY0evIv.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/6PLCjrQT0fnxwEVVzPGO.png\"]', '2024-01-16 10:32:31', '2024-01-16 10:32:31', 1, 'hotel-colline', NULL, 'Located in the heart of Dalat city, 1640 feet from Lam Vien Square, Hôtel Colline provides a bar and rooms with free WiFi access. This hotel is located 656 feet from Xuan Huong Lake. The hotel has a restaurant, and Yersin Park Da Lat is 1640 feet away.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.440869882379!2d108.43323067718323!3d11.943948158078232!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3171135333d87745%3A0xef770fc699bf659b!2sH%C3%B4tel%20Colline!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705401123939!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laun