(112, 'Golf Valley Hotel', '94 Đường Bùi Thị Xuân, Phường 2, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 670000, Vietnam', 5, '02633697666', NULL, 'https://golfvalleyhotel.com/', '<p>Located in Da Lat, 1.2 miles from Dalat Palace Golf Club, Golf Valley Hotel has accommodations with a fitness center, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests. At the hotel rooms are equipped with air conditioning, a desk, a balcony with a city view, a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV, bed linen and towels. The rooms will provide guests with a fridge. You can play darts at Golf Valley Hotel, and car rental is available. Lam Vien Square is 1.1 miles from the accommodation, while Xuan Huong Lake is 1.3 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 17 miles from Golf Valley Hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/C4ldqBoPOiuAQBbfxul6.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/JvHSd8qOO4Vc7M9NhmMT.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:15:11', '2024-01-17 01:15:11', 1, 'golf-valley-hotel', NULL, 'Located in Da Lat, 1.2 miles from Dalat Palace Golf Club, Golf Valley Hotel has accommodations with a fitness center, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Among the facilities of this property are a restaurant, a kids\' club and room service, along with free WiFi. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.389191657757!2d108.43573257718354!3d11.94753355806636!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31711396844f2267%3A0x745002ebb2d69574!2sGolf%20Valley%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454089732!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL