(113, 'Cherry House Đà Lạt', 'Hẻm 31Nguyễn Công Trứ, Phường 8, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 67000, Vietnam', 4, '0972336279', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/cherryhousedl', '<p>Cherry House Đ&agrave; Lạt is located in Da Lat, a 9-minute walk from Dalat Palace Golf Club and one mile from Dalat Flower Gardens. Among the facilities at this property are room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides a concierge service, a tour desk and luggage storage for guests. At the hotel, rooms are equipped with a desk, a terrace with a city view, a private bathroom, a flat-screen TV, bed linen and towels. Cherry House Đ&agrave; Lạt has some accommodations that have a balcony, and each room is equipped with an electric tea pot. The rooms include a closet. Xuan Huong Lake is 2 miles from the accommodation, while Yersin Park is 2 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 19 miles from Cherry House Đ&agrave; Lạt.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/YzAMOCeQamPOJqRVnyUd.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/2iHDhnLFcVo1ypIV9uZL.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:16:50', '2024-01-17 01:16:50', 1, 'cherry-house-da-lat', NULL, 'Cherry House Đà Lạt is located in Da Lat, a 9-minute walk from Dalat Palace Golf Club and one mile from Dalat Flower Gardens. Among the facilities at this property are room service and a 24-hour front desk, along with free WiFi throughout the property. The property provides a concierge service, a tour desk and luggage storage for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.28954493186!2d108.43751517473005!3d11.954443988275212!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317112da16bbc24f%3A0x1cf76b820e724caf!2sCherry%20House%20Dalat!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454188710!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"