(114, 'New Century Dalat Hotel', '14B Đường Đống Đa, Phường 3, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 670000, Vietnam', 5, '0776458485', NULL, NULL, '<p>Located in Da Lat, within 1.7 miles of Yersin Park and 1.7 miles of Xuan Huong Lake, New Century Dalat Hotel has accommodations with a restaurant and free WiFi as well as free private parking for guests who drive. This 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. The hotel provides a hot tub and luggage storage space. The rooms at the hotel come with a seating area, a flat-screen TV with cable channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. The rooms include an electric tea pot, while certain rooms come with a balcony and others also feature city views. At New Century Dalat Hotel rooms have bed linen and towels. Lam Vien Square is 1.9 miles from the accommodation, while Truc Lam Temple is 2.8 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong, 16 miles from New Century Dalat Hotel, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/rX2pNgPHwhyqy5csexLP.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/k72N1cfl4iuKLrt8F4B9.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:18:12', '2024-01-17 01:18:12', 1, 'new-century-dalat-hotel', NULL, 'Located in Da Lat, within 1.7 miles of Yersin Park and 1.7 miles of Xuan Huong Lake, New Century Dalat Hotel has accommodations with a restaurant and free WiFi as well as free private parking for guests who drive. This 4-star hotel offers room service and a 24-hour front desk. The hotel provides a hot tub and luggage storage space.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.732785676231!2d108.44066027472957!3d11.923675288303606!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317113e107fce7ff%3A0xc71b8918d8f2da4b!2sNew%20Century%20Dalat%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454271074!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-r