(115, 'Bình Dương Đà Lạt Hotel', '36k Đ. Hùng Vương, Phường 9, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 66000, Vietnam', 4, '02633997979', NULL, 'http://xn--khchsnbnhdnglthotel-hubk1wt5av8hyk1435dna.com/', '<p>Featuring 3-star accommodations, B&igrave;nh Dương Đ&agrave; Lạt Hotel is located in Da Lat, 1.4 miles from Dalat Flower Gardens and 1.7 miles from Xuan Huong Lake. The property is around 1.7 miles from Yersin Park, 1.8 miles from Dalat Palace Golf Club and 1.8 miles from Lam Vien Square. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, an ATM and free WiFi. At the hotel, the rooms include a desk. Featuring a private bathroom with a bidet and free toiletries, rooms at B&igrave;nh Dương Đ&agrave; Lạt Hotel also feature a city view. All rooms in the accommodation are equipped with a flat-screen TV and a hairdryer. Tuyen Lam Lake is 4.9 miles from B&igrave;nh Dương Đ&agrave; Lạt Hotel, while Truc Lam Temple is 5.2 miles from the property. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 19 miles from the hotel.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/ytrUNEMEMorJZC84Xbns.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/839cAB5R8SvdVvpRxR2t.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:21:33', '2024-01-17 01:21:33', 1, 'binh-duong-da-lat-hotel', NULL, 'Featuring 3-star accommodations, Bình Dương Đà Lạt Hotel is located in Da Lat, 1.4 miles from Dalat Flower Gardens and 1.7 miles from Xuan Huong Lake. The property is around 1.7 miles from Yersin Park, 1.8 miles from Dalat Palace Golf Club and 1.8 miles from Lam Vien Square. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, an ATM and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3903.3957718420083!2d108.46372257472986!3d11.947077088281986!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x317113f024e6ac91%3A0x926af76aaee6cada!2zS2jDoWNoIFPhuqFuIELDrG5oIETGsMahbmctIMSQw6AgTOG6oXQgaG90ZWw!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454471368!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" refe