(116, 'Dalat Wonder Resort', 'VCV9+R9, Phường 4, Thành phố Đà Lạt, Lâm Đồng 66100, Vietnam', 5, '02633800099', NULL, 'http://www.dalatwonderresort.com/', '<p>Located in Da Lat, 4.4 miles from Truc Lam Temple, Dalat Wonder Resort provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Featuring room service, this property also has a restaurant and a terrace. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a shared kitchen and free WiFi. Every room comes with a private bathroom, while some rooms here will provide you with a balcony and others also provide guests with a lake view. You can play pool at this 4-star resort, and the area is popular for hiking. Tuyen Lam Lake is 4.4 miles from the resort, while Lam Vien Square is 6.2 miles away. The nearest airport is Lien Khuong Airport, 19 miles from Dalat Wonder Resort.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/CJkHGYHqnHS38gdvmqwl.png', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/NCKvze8g40tqTIrBFRzm.png\"]', '2024-01-17 01:23:22', '2024-01-17 01:23:22', 1, 'dalat-wonder-resort', NULL, 'Located in Da Lat, 4.4 miles from Truc Lam Temple, Dalat Wonder Resort provides accommodations with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a fitness center and a garden. Featuring room service, this property also has a restaurant and a terrace. The property has a 24-hour front desk, airport transportation, a shared kitchen and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3904.1293828870316!2d108.41197127472897!3d11.896077988329058!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31716b5e240fdce9%3A0x84da3e5245e8a947!2sDalat%20Wonder%20Resort!5e0!3m2!1sen!2s!4v1705454579810!5m2!1sen!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"p