(124, 'The Leaf Boutique', '38 Võ Nguyên Giáp 38 Vo Nguyen Giap Str, Man Thai Ward, Son Tra Dist, Danang City, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363669333', NULL, 'http://www.theleafdanang.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Set in Da Nang, a few steps from My Khe Beach, The Leaf Boutique offers accommodation with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Offering a bar, the property is located within 3.8 km of Song Han Bridge. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi. All guest rooms at the hotel come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a bidet, free toiletries and a hairdryer. All rooms include a kettle, while certain rooms also offer a kitchen with a fridge and a microwave. At The Leaf Boutique the rooms come with bed linen and towels. A buffet, &agrave; la carte or continental breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 4.3 km from the accommodation, while Indochina Riverside Mall is 4.6 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 8 km from The Leaf Boutique.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.9</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/f3nQCBJAqTK2UdXRy3Fh.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/Z8eQhdT5MBsFD4wJD6Jg.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:06:41', '2024-01-17 07:06:41', 1, 'the-leaf-boutique', NULL, 'Set in Da Nang, a few steps from My Khe Beach, The Leaf Boutique offers accommodation with an outdoor swimming pool, free private parking, a shared lounge and a terrace. Offering a bar, the property is located within 3.8 km of Song Han Bridge. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.6074794372394!2d108.24556387415177!3d16.085846084596046!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142173a22bf7925%3A0x1fa7d67836459fa8!2sThe%20Leaf%20Boutique%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705475095251!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(125, 'San Marino Boutique DaNang', '161-163-165 Vo Van Kiet, Son Tra, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363985777', NULL, 'http://sanmarinodanang.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">In a prime location in the My Khe Beach, San Marino Boutique Danang offers a restaurant, terrace and sea views. Guests can enjoy free WiFi in entire property. All units at the hotel are equipped with a seating area and a flat-screen TV. The rooms are equipped with a private bathroom with free toiletries, while some rooms include a balcony and others also have river views. The units will provide guests with a fridge. Breakfast with Asian and Western dishes can be selected from the menus. Staff speak English and Vietnamese at the 24-hour front desk. Free airport drop off is provided. Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 900 metres from San Marino Boutique Danang, while Cham Museum is 1.6 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International, 5 km from the accommodation.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.0</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/QtzZQj0sq1ertykBq2Gu.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/W7uK0v1CsCPhTPB6toGr.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:09:01', '2024-01-17 07:09:01', 1, 'san-marino-boutique-danang', NULL, 'In a prime location in the My Khe Beach, San Marino Boutique Danang offers a restaurant, terrace and sea views. Guests can enjoy free WiFi in entire property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d9119.070798108314!2d108.23477373220634!3d16.060456900711905!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142177fe2b834d7%3A0xbabc9b33cf003c41!2sSan%20Marino%20Boutique%20DaNang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705475314291!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(126, 'Hotel Del Luna Boutique', '138 Ho Nghinh, Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363272569', NULL, 'http://hoteldelluna.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Set in Da Nang, 500 metres from My Khe Beach, Hotel Del Luna Boutique offers accommodation with a terrace, free private parking, a restaurant and a bar. The property is situated 2.1 km from Song Han Bridge, 2.6 km from Love Lock Bridge Da Nang and 2.9 km from Indochina Riverside Mall. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, a concierge service and free WiFi. All guest rooms come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a kettle, a bidet, free toiletries and a wardrobe. With a private bathroom fitted with a shower and a hairdryer, some units at the hotel also have a city view. At Hotel Del Luna Boutique all rooms have bed linen and towels. A buffet, &agrave; la carte or American breakfast can be enjoyed at the property. The accommodation offers 4-star accommodation with an indoor pool, sauna and hot tub. Hotel Del Luna Boutique provides a dry cleaning service, as well as business facilities like fax and photocopying. Cham Museum is 3.4 km from the hotel, while Asia Park Danang is 6.8 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 6 km from Hotel Del Luna Boutique.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.9</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/qvb38qk3lj132DWFNFXW.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/7GMUcQFETQbvNmrqLEDU.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:11:49', '2024-01-17 07:11:49', 1, 'hotel-del-luna-boutique', NULL, 'Set in Da Nang, 500 metres from My Khe Beach, Hotel Del Luna Boutique offers accommodation with a terrace, free private parking, a restaurant and a bar. The property is situated 2.1 km from Song Han Bridge, 2.6 km from Love Lock Bridge Da Nang and 2.9 km from Indochina Riverside Mall. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, a concierge service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3833.8578841577605!2d108.24026887415141!3d16.072862884607165!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142174dcb1e9e55%3A0xb4edb064f853690d!2zSG90ZWwgRGVsIEx1bmEgLSBLaMOhY2ggc-G6oW4gw4FuaCBUcsSDbmc!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705475463944!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(127, 'HAIAN Riverfront Hotel Da Nang', '182 Bach Dang , Da Nang, Vietnam', 4, '02363573888', NULL, 'https://www.haianriverfronthotel.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Ideally situated in the centre of Da Nang, HAIAN Riverfront Hotel Da Nang features air-conditioned rooms, a fitness centre, free WiFi and a terrace. Featuring a restaurant, the property also has a bar, as well as an indoor pool. The accommodation provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and currency exchange for guests. All rooms at the hotel are fitted with a seating area, a flat-screen TV and a safety deposit box. The rooms have a kettle and a private bathroom with a bidet and free toiletries, while some rooms are fitted with a kitchen fitted with a fridge. At HAIAN Riverfront Hotel Da Nang rooms are fitted with bed linen and towels. Popular points of interest near the accommodation include Indochina Riverside Mall, Cham Museum and Song Han Bridge. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 4 km from HAIAN Riverfront Hotel Da Nang.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.6</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/jBkgUIQEaqcxRPayOWcj.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/XkuszAQfWOXCJcfK6mGC.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:13:59', '2024-01-17 07:13:59', 1, 'haian-riverfront-hotel-da-nang', NULL, 'Ideally situated in the centre of Da Nang, HAIAN Riverfront Hotel Da Nang features air-conditioned rooms, a fitness centre, free WiFi and a terrace. Featuring a restaurant, the property also has a bar, as well as an indoor pool. The accommodation provides room service, a 24-hour front desk and c