(131, 'Cozy Danang Boutique Hotel', '37 Co Giang, Danang, Vietnam', 4, '02363658666', NULL, 'http://cozydananghotel.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Ideally located in the center of Danang, Cozy Danang Boutique Hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, free private parking and room service. Among the various facilities are an outdoor swimming pool, a shared lounge, as well as a terrace. The property provides a 24-hour front desk, a concierge service and currency exchange for guests. At the hotel, the rooms have a desk, a flat-screen TV, a private bathroom, bed linen and towels. Rooms have a safety deposit box, while selected rooms also feature a balcony and others also feature city views. All rooms in Cozy Danang Boutique Hotel are equipped with free toiletries and an iPod docking station. Guests at the accommodation will be able to enjoy activities in and around Danang, like cycling. Popular points of interest near Cozy Danang Boutique Hotel include Cham Museum, Indochina Riverside Mall and Love Lock Bridge Da Nang. The nearest airport is Da Nang International, 1.2 miles from the hotel, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples in particular like the location &ndash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.4</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/7NWbthMZvw8kDjldV6yJ.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/TDS9MGczBkTlMQoo69Am.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:23:26', '2024-01-17 07:23:26', 1, 'cozy-danang-boutique-hotel', NULL, 'Ideally located in the center of Danang, Cozy Danang Boutique Hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, free private parking and room service. Among the 