(133, 'Risemount Premier Resort Da Nang', '120 Nguyễn Văn Thoại Bac My An ward, Ngu Hanh Son district, Danang, Vietnam', 4, '02363899999', NULL, NULL, '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<h3 class=\"top_pick_heading\">Experience World-class Service at Risemount Premier Resort Da Nang</h3>\r\n<div data-component=\"content-agency/property-desc-tracker/property-desc-tracker\">&nbsp;</div>\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">You\'re eligible for a Genius discount at Risemount Premier Resort Da Nang! To save at this property, all you have to do is&nbsp;<a class=\"bui-link\" href=\"https://account.booking.com/auth/oauth2?state=UvoBAtgUCCRlYpXMWV2TmmS7LKcgOVVbA15JKt1MiXoWEDvm02AY4UqCeldPrWejSn9tt-C_lco3txyx8tewbjJ_jhEMynntnpDT0rdglrQfGTJxKM9yEiUwdysWKnQ9jdlzubxqDbVggN1OZoaAQU56Qj-iJO9PED6ATCFWfsDBuZP9XpUQOgbrvLsvUWzZWfTryxDt3P_epmb4ucBPpygdaETMzfFo4bF443SU8vMfToVXUehTPOTemsrCmV9Xs5s3FS4V7J9Q7Uce0uz_NsvOZG2AHUVdziegjtXdowxOvaSq2IarHP2r148Bu3y2qxzQEABQGmOfx_oGtw&amp;aid=357028&amp;bkng_action=hotel&amp;lang=en-us&amp;dt=1705476366&amp;redirect_uri=https%3A%2F%2Fsecure.booking.com%2Flogin.html%3Fop%3Doauth_return&amp;client_id=vO1Kblk7xX9tUn2cpZLS&amp;response_type=sso\" data-et-click=\"customGoal:eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">sign in</a>.</p>\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Located in the My Khe Beach district in Da Nang, 1640 feet from My An Beach, Risemount Resort Danang features two outdoor pools and barbecue. The resort has a fitness center and spa center, coupled with a hot tub and a sauna. Air-conditioned units at the resort are equipped with a seating area, flat-screen TV with satellite channels and private bathroom with free toiletries. Certain units offer a private balcony, kitchen or free WiFi. A business cen