(134, 'Bliss Luxury Hotel & Spa', '30 An Đồn 6, An Hải Bắc, quận Sơn Trà, Da Nang, Vietnam', 3, '0982274656', NULL, NULL, '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<p data-et-view=\"eWHMcCcCcCSYeJbNXGDJdcSNDeMSZGSRaPSZbRe:1\">Featuring luxurious interior decor, Bliss Luxury Hotel &amp; Spa offers stylish accommodation in picturesque Da Nang. Guests at the property can enjoy an array of cuisines from the on-site restaurant, or choose your favourite drink off the on-site bar\'s menu. A swimming pool and fitness centre are available for your convenience. Free WiFi is available throughout the property. Each room at the property features modern decor in neutral and soothing shades. Each room comes with a work desk and/or seating area, as well as a wardrobe. The en-suite bathroom comes fitted with a standing shower facility. The property features barbecue facilities, a tour and ticketing desk, as well as meeting/banquet facilities. Bilingual staff are available 24 hours a day at the front desk to assist you with services such as luggage storage, concierge and other enquiries. The hotel also offers free use of bicycles and electric tourist car to the beach with fixed schedule. Guests who drive may choose to reserve a free public parking space nearby. Usage of the massage facilities are available at a surcharge. Song Han Bridge is 1.2 km away from Bliss Luxury Hotel &amp; Spa, while Han Market is 1.5 km away.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.3</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/sdvyuH5Ji48VsVpVcfkK.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/ZvPcX8wCMi3AjhdBymyZ.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:30:35', '2024-01-17 07:30:35', 0, 'bliss-luxury-hotel-and-spa', NULL, 'Featuring luxurious interior decor, Bliss Luxury Hotel & Spa offers stylish accommodation in picturesque Da Nang. Guests at the property can enjoy an array of cuisines from the on-site restaurant, or choose your favourite drink off the on-site bar\'s menu. A swimming pool and fitness centre are available for your convenience. Free WiFi is available throughout the property.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d7667.889454317898!2d108.22490383791134!3d16.068357788443816!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314217724a4fa4ed%3A0x5b65297c938ec97d!2sBliss%20Luxury%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705476591429!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(135, 'Pandora Hotel Da Nang', '21-23 Phan Tôn, phường Mỹ An, Quận Ngũ Hành Sơn, Đà Nẵng, Da Nang, Vietnam', 3, '02363911169', NULL, 'https://www.pandorahoteldn.com.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Pandora Hotel Da Nang has a restaurant, free bicycles, an outdoor swimming pool and fitness centre in Da Nang. With a bar, the 4-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests. All rooms at the hotel are fitted with a seating area and a flat-screen TV. The rooms will provide guests with a wardrobe and a kettle. A continental breakfast is available each morning at Pandora Hotel Da Nang. The accommodation offers a terrace. The area is popular for hiking and cycling, and car hire is available at Pandora Hotel Da Nang. My Khe Beach is 250 metres from the hotel, while Bac My An Beach is 1.5 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International, 5 km from Pandora Hotel Da Nang, and the property offers a paid airport shuttle service.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.6</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/0hjUpUwvdxR4kxrP80Sx.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/rLHYZepsYhdSpNCQQ3ff.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:33:10', '2024-01-17 07:33:10', 1, 'pandora-hotel-da-nang', NULL, 'Pandora Hotel Da Nang has a restaurant, free bicycles, an outdoor swimming pool and fitness centre in Da Nang. With a bar, the 4-star hotel has air-conditioned rooms with free WiFi, each with a private bathroom. The accommodation features a 24-hour front desk, room service and currency exchange for guests.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3834.248245819671!2d108.24319717415098!3d16.05260268462446!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314217ecbcdaaf17%3A0x26c7314a2ca1b8c0!2sPandora%20Boutique%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705476753254!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(136, 'Adaline Hotel and Suite', '45-47 Vo Van Kiet , Son Tra District, Da Nang City, Da Nang, Vietnam', 3, '02363666567', NULL, 'https://www.facebook.com/adalinehoteldanang/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Offering an outdoor pool and views of the sea, Adaline Hotel and Suite is situated in Da Nang in the Da Nang Municipality Region, 2.1 km from Song Han Bridge. Guests can enjoy the on-site restaurant. Free WiFi is provided and free private parking is available on site. Every room at this hotel is air conditioned and features a flat-screen TV. You will find a kettle in the room. Each room includes a private bathroom. For your comfort, you will find slippers, free toiletries and a hairdryer. There is a 24-hour front desk at the property. The hotel also offers bike hire and car hire. Indochina Riverside Mall is 2.1 km from Adaline Hotel and Suite, while Cham Museum is 2.2 km away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 5 km from Adaline Hotel and Suite.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.1</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/tKuCgmMycJg65TCKF4qW.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/pKvNL3rTXVzNy3JFY340.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:35:50', '2024-01-17 07:35:50', 1, 'adaline-hotel-and-suite', NULL, 'Offering an outdoor pool and views of the sea, Adaline Hotel and Suite is situated in Da Nang in the Da Nang Municipality Region, 2.1 km from Song Han Bridge. Guests can enjoy the on-site restaurant. Free WiFi is provided and free private parking is available on site.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3834.0442849015026!2d108.24116407415129!3d16.063191584615403!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x314217821e64262b%3A0x61a9113df756b76c!2sAdaline%20Hotel%20%26%20Suite!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705476911678!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(137, 'Sepon Blue Hotel', '157-159 Võ Văn Kiệt, Da Nang, Vietnam', 3, '02363679999', NULL, 'http://www.seponblue.com/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Facing the beachfront, Sepon Blue Hotel offers 4-star accommodation in Da Nang and features an outdoor swimming pool, shared lounge and terrace. The property has a bar, as well as a restaurant serving Asian cuisine. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi. The units come with air conditioning, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a fridge, a kettle, a shower, free toiletries and a desk. All rooms are equipped with a private bathroom with a hairdryer, while some rooms come with a patio and others also have sea views. At the hotel each room comes with bed linen and towels. Sepon Blue Hotel offers a buffet or Asian breakfast. My Khe Beach is 1.7 km from the accommodation, while Bac My An Beach is 2.2 km away. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 5 km from Sepon Blue Hotel.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>9.1</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/YcCG9IxcvnG7mMvUsJjn.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/zp63R9CzAc4Hra48Zu6C.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:38:10', '2024-01-17 07:38:10', 1, 'sepon-blue-hotel', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Sepon Blue Hotel offers 4-star accommodation in Da Nang and features an outdoor swimming pool, shared lounge and terrace. The property has a bar, as well as a restaurant serving Asian cuisine. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d3834.0712049412264!2d108.23516547415116!3d16.06179438461663!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x31421781e7fc2e4b%3A0xb61c4f5316b30aa0!2sSepon%20Blue%20Hotel!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705477064304!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16),
(138, 'Angel Hotels Beach Danang', 'Lot 31, 32 Ngo Thi Si, My An, Ngu Hanh Son, Da Nang, Viet nam, Da Nang, Vietnam', 3, '02363958558', NULL, 'http://angelhotels.vn/', '<div id=\"summary\" class=\"hotel_description_review_display\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div id=\"property_description_content\" data-et-view=\"\">\r\n<div data-capla-component-boundary=\"b-property-web-property-page/PropertyDescriptionDesktop\">\r\n<p class=\"a53cbfa6de b3efd73f69\">Facing the beachfront, Angel Hotels Beach Danang offers 4-star accommodation in Da Nang and has an outdoor swimming pool, terrace and restaurant. Boasting a bar, the hotel is close to several noted attractions, around 100 metres from My Khe Beach and around 500 metres from Bac My An Beach. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi. At the hotel the rooms come with air conditioning, a seating area, a flat-screen TV with satellite channels, a safety deposit box and a private bathroom with a shower, free toiletries and a hairdryer. Angel Hotels Beach Danang features some units with city views, and all rooms come with a kettle. At the accommodation the rooms have bed linen and towels. Angel Hotels Beach Danang offers an American or Asian breakfast. Love Lock Bridge Da Nang is 3.5 km from the hotel, while Asia Park Danang is 3.9 km from the property. The nearest airport is Da Nang International Airport, 7 km from Angel Hotels Beach Danang.</p>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n</div>\r\n<p class=\"hp-desc-review-highlight hp-desc-traveller-type--ph-v0\">Couples particularly like the location &mdash; they rated it&nbsp;<strong>8.8</strong>&nbsp;for a two-person trip.</p>', 'hotels/January2024/Fcyte3Qu2fD8yCY6DgFp.jpg', '[\"hotels\\/January2024\\/7lQZ0QyFPbJEkPnXEyFc.jpg\"]', '2024-01-17 07:40:11', '2024-01-17 07:40:11', 1, 'angel-hotels-beach-danang', NULL, 'Facing the beachfront, Angel Hotels Beach Danang offers 4-star accommodation in Da Nang and has an outdoor swimming pool, terrace and restaurant. Boasting a bar, the hotel is close to several noted attractions, around 100 metres from My Khe Beach and around 500 metres from Bac My An Beach. The accommodation offers a 24-hour front desk, airport transfers, room service and free WiFi.', '<iframe src=\"https://www.google.com/maps/embed?pb=!1m18!1m12!1m3!1d4559.815659437723!2d108.24578333046887!3d16.04821914338307!2m3!1f0!2f0!3f0!3m2!1i1024!2i768!4f13.1!3m3!1m2!1s0x3142172ca2a8847d%3A0x17ae14f4a51a4f97!2sAngel%20Hotels%20Beach%20Danang!5e0!3m2!1svi!2s!4v1705477178662!5m2!1svi!2s\" width=\"600\" height=\"450\" style=\"border:0;\" allowfullscreen=\"\" loading=\"lazy\" referrerpolicy=\"no-referrer-when-downgrade\"></iframe>', NULL, '{\"247\":\"247\",\"restaurant\":\"restaurant\",\"internet\":\"internet\",\"spa\":\"spa\",\"pool\":\"pool\",\"parking\":\"parking\",\"laundry\":\"laundry\",\"room_service\":\"room_service\",\"meeting_room\":\"meeting_room\",\"luggage_storage\":\"luggage_storage\"}', 16);

